<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2297">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2297">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2298">Įvykis įrašomas, kai vykdoma failo atidarymo operacija, ir naudojamas siekiant suprasti ir nustatyti prioritetus vartotojo patirčiai remiantis failo atidarymo operacijos informacija, pvz., vietinėmis kategorijomis „ServiceType“ ir pirmaisiais keturiais plėtinio simboliais.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2298">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories "ServiceType" and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2299">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2299">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2300">**Data_Ext** – failo plėtinys, apribotas iki pirmų keturių ar mažiau plėtinio simbolių.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2300">**Data_Ext** - The file extension limited to the first four characters of the extension or less.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2301">**Data_ServiceType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2301">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_fileoperations_opendocumentmeasurements"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2302">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_OpenDocumentMeasurements</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2302">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_OpenDocumentMeasurements</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2303">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „iOS“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2303">This event is collected for Office applications running under iOS platform.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2304">Įvykių įrašai, kai vykdoma failo atidarymo operacija, naudojami suprasti ir nustatyti prioritetus vartotojo patirčiai pagal failo atidarymo operacijos informaciją ir ypač efektyvumo informaciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2304">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information, especially performance information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2305">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2305">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2306">**Data_AppDuration** – taikomosios programos apdorojimo trukmė atliekant failo atidarymo operaciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2306">**Data_AppDuration** - The duration spent in application processing during a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2307">**Data_BootDuration** – failo atidarymo paleidimo proceso trukmė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2307">**Data_BootDuration** - The duration of boot process of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2308">**Data_ClickOrigin** – eilutė, rodanti, saito dalį, kurią vartotojas spustelėjo „iOS Outlook“, kad atidaryti failą „Office“ programoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2308">**Data_ClickOrigin** - A string indicating which part the link was from when user clicked a link in iOS Outlook to open a file in Office app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2309">**Data_ClickTime** – „Unix“ laikotarpis, kai vartotojas spustelėjo saitą „iOS Outlook“, kad atidaryti failą programoje „Office“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2309">**Data_ClickTime** - The Unix epoch time when the user clicked a link in iOS Outlook to open the file in Office app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2310">**Data_ClosePreviouslyOpenedMarkers** – eilutės reikšmė, fiksuojanti laiką tarp tam tikrų funkcijų iškvietimų, pateikiama formatu su funkcijos ID ir trukme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2310">**Data_ClosePreviouslyOpenedMarkers** – A string value logging the time duration between some function calls, in a format with function id and duration.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2311">**Data_DetachedDuration** – įvykio atsiejimo proceso trukmė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2311">**Data_DetachedDuration** - The duration of detach process of an event.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2312">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – išvardijimas, rodantis failo prieigos režimą, pvz., tik skaityti, skaityti / rašyti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2312">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, e.g. read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2313">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – išvardijimas, rodantis, kokio tipo asinchroninis srautas naudojamas failui atidaryti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2313">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** - An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2314">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – išvardijimas, rodantis failo segmentavimo algoritmą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2314">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - An enumeration indicating the type of chunking algorithm of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2315">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – išvardijimas, rodantis įmonės duomenų failo apsaugos būseną.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2315">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - An enumeration indicating the enterprise data protection state of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2316">**Data_Doc_Ext** – failo plėtinys.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2316">**Data_Doc_Ext** - File extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2317">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – failo serverio pagrindinio kompiuterio pavadinimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2317">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2318">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – GUID, kuris unikaliai identifikuoja serverio pagrindinio kompiuterio pavadinimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2318">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2319">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – GUID, kuris unikaliai identifikuoja tapatybę, naudojamą failui atidaryti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2319">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the identity used to open a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2320">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – išvardijimas, rodantis išsamius failo atidarymo operacijos scenarijaus tipus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2320">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - An enumeration indicating the detailed scenario type of a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2321">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – išvardijimas, rodantis failo atidarymo operacijos įvesties ir išvesties žymes, pvz., ar failas yra talpykloje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2321">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - An enumeration indicating the IO flags of a file open operation, e.g. if the file is cached or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2322">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** – ar šiam failui įgalintas bendradarbiavimas debesyje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2322">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** - Whether or not the cloud collaboration is enabled for the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2323">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – ar failas buvo atidarytas naudojant papildantįjį atidarymą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2323">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened via incremental open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2324">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – ar failas palaiko „Office“ bendradarbiavimo tarnybą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2324">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Whether or not a file supports Office Collaboration Service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2325">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – ar failas atidaromas iš autonominėje talpykloje laikomos kopijos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2325">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Whether or not a file is opened from an offline cached copy.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2326">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** – ar failas buvo paimtas iš anksto prieš atidarymo operacijos atlikimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2326">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** - Whether or not the file was prefetched before open operation happened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2327">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – ar debesies failas yra lokaliai ir ar sinchronizuojamas su serveriu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2327">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Whether or not a cloud file exists locally and is synchronized with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2328">**Data_Doc_Location** – išvardijimas, rodantis failo vietą, pvz., lokalus arba debesyje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2328">**Data_Doc_Location** - An enumeration indicating where the file is located, e.g. locally or in cloud.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2329">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – išvardijimas, rodantis failo priežastį tik skaityti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2329">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - An enumeration indicating the read only reason of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2330">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** – GUID, unikaliai identifikuojantis failo serverio išteklių ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2330">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server resource id of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2331">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – išvardijimas, rodantis failo naudojamą realaus laiko kanalo (RTC) tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2331">**Data_Doc_RtcType** - An enumeration indicating type of real-time channel (RTC) used by the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2332">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – GUID, kuris unikaliai identifikuoja serverio dokumento ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2332">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server document ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2333">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – išvardijimas, rodantis debesies failo serverio protokolą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2333">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - An enumeration indicating the server protocol of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2334">**Data_Doc_ServerType** – išvardijimas, rodantis debesies failo serverio tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2334">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - An enumeration indicating the server type of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2335">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – išvardijimas, rodantis debesies failo serverio versiją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2335">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - An enumeration indicating the server version of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2336">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – sveikasis skaičius, padidėjantis 1 kiekvieną kartą, kai seanso metu atliekama failo atidarymo operacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2336">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - An integer which is incremented by 1 for each file open operation in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2337">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – eilutė, naudojama susieti kliento ir serverio žurnalus, paprastai tai yra ID tipas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2337">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - A string used to correlate client-side and server-side logs, typically it is a kind of ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2338">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – dokumento dydis baitais.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2338">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - File size in bytes.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2339">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – išvardijimas, rodantis URL failo specialųjį simbolį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2339">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - An enumeration indicating which kind of special character the file URL has.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2340">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – GUID, kuris unikaliai identifikuoja failo URL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2340">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the file URL.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2341">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** – ar failas buvo atidarytas palaipsniui naudojant iš anksto talpykloje saugomus WRS duomenis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2341">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened incrementally using pre-cached WRS data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2342">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** – eilutė, rodanti iš kurios tarnybos yra WOPI (žiniatinklio taikomosios programos atviro platformos sąsajos protokolas) failas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2342">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - A string indicating which service a WOPI (Web Application Open Platform Interface Protocol) file is from.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2343">**Data_HWModel** – eilutės reikšmė, kuri registruoja „iPad“ arba „iPhone“ įrenginio modelį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2343">**Data_HWModel** – A string value logging the model of iPad or iPhone device.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2344">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** – eilutės reikšmė, fiksuojanti laiką, sugaištą atliekant tam tikrus funkcijų iškvietimus. Pateikiama formatu: su funkcijos žyme ir trukme, kuri apima papildomų funkcijų iškvietimų trukmę.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2344">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which includes the duration of sub-function calls.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2345">**Data_InitializationReason** – išvardijimas, rodantis kaip failas atidaromas, pvz., iš kurio vartotojo sąsajos elemento arba paleistas kitos taikomosios programos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2345">**Data_InitializationReason** - An enumeration indicating how the file is opened, e.g. from which UI element or triggered by another app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2346">**Data_IsDocumentAlreadyOpen** – ar failas jau atidarytas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2346">**Data_IsDocumentAlreadyOpen** – Whether or not the file is already open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2347">**Data_IsInterrupted** – ar failo atidarymo operacija buvo nutraukta, kai programa perėjo prie fono.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2347">**Data_IsInterrupted** – Whether or not the file open operation was interrupted by app transitioning to background.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2348">**Data_Measurements** – eilutės reikšmė, fiksuojanti laiką, sugaištą atliekant tam tikrus funkcijų iškvietimus. Pateikiama formatu: su funkcijos žyme ir trukme, neapimančia papildomų funkcijų iškvietimų trukmės.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2348">**Data_Measurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which excludes the duration of sub-function calls.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2349">**Data_OpenInPlace** – ar failas turi būti kopijuojamas į „Office“ smėlio dėžės talpyklą, kad vartotojas galėtų jį atidaryti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2349">**Data_OpenInPlace** - Whether or not a file must be copied to the Office's sandboxed container before user can open it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2350">**Data_OpenStartTime** – „Unix“ laikotarpis, kai prasidėjo failo atidarymas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2350">**Data_OpenStartTime** - The Unix epoch time when the file open started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2351">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** – failo atidarymo generavimo trukmė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2351">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** - The duration of rendering of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2352">**Data_SourceApplication** – eilutė, nurodanti šaltinio taikomosios programos grupavimo ID, kai failas atidaromas naudojant kitą taikomąją programą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2352">**Data_SourceApplication** - A string indicating the bundle ID of the source application when a file open was triggered by another app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2353">**Data_StopwatchDuration** – trukmė nuo įvykio pradžios iki pabaigos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2353">**Data_StopwatchDuration** - The duration from beginning of the event to the end of the event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2354">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements** – eilutės reikšmė, fiksuojanti laiką, sugaištą atliekant tam tikrus funkcijų iškvietimus. Pateikiama formatu: su funkcijos žyme, pradžios laiko žyma ir trukme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2354">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag, start timestamp and duration.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_fileoperations_openfilewithreason"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2355">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_OpenFileWithReason</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2355">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_OpenFileWithReason</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2356">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2356">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2357">Įvykis įrašomas, kai vykdoma failo atidarymo operacija, ir naudojamas siekiant suprasti ir nustatyti prioritetus vartotojo patirčiai remiantis failo atidarymo operacijos informacija, pvz., vietinėmis kategorijomis „ServiceType“ ir kurioje programos vietoje naudotojas pateikė prašymą atidaryti failą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2357">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories "ServiceType" and from where within Application the user requested to open a file.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2358">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2358">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2359">**Data_IsCandidateDropboxFile** – tai yra Bulio logikos reikšmė, kuri registruojama, jei tikrinant failo kelią, manome, kad jis gali būti iš aplanko, kuris sinchronizuotas saugyklos „DropBox“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2359">**Data_IsCandidateDropboxFile** - This is a Boolean value that is logged if by inspecting the path of the file we think it might be from a folder that is sync'd by Drop Box.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2360">**Data_IsSignedIn** – ar failo įrašymo metu vartotojas yra prisijungęs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2360">**Data_IsSignedIn** - Whether or not a user is signed in when the file is saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2361">**Data_OpenReason** – atviroji priežastis yra skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti vietą, iš kurios taikomojoje programoje vartotojas atidarė failą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2361">**Data_OpenReason** - The open reason is a numerical value that indicates from where within the application a user opened a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2362">**Data_ServiceType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus skaitinis kategorizavimas, ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2362">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract numerical categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_fileoperations_savetourl"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2363">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_SaveToURL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2363">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_SaveToURL</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2364">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2364">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2365">Įvykis įrašomas, kai vykdoma operacija „įrašyti kaip“, ir naudojamas siekiant suprasti ir nustatyti prioritetus vartotojo patirčiai remiantis failo operacijos informacija, pvz., vietinėmis kategorijomis ir pirmaisiais keturiais plėtinio simboliais.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2365">The event records when a "save as" operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file operation information such as location categories and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2366">Operacija „įrašyti kaip“ vykdoma, kai vartotojas sukuria naują failą ir įrašo jį pirmą kartą arba išsaugo esamo failo kopiją naujoje vietoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2366">A "save as" operation occurs whenever a user creates a new file and saves it for the first time or saves a copy of an existing file to a new location.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2367">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2367">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2368">**Data_FileExtension** – pirmi keturi naujo failo plėtinio simboliai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2368">**Data_FileExtension** - The first four characters of the new file's extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2369">**Data_IsNewFileCreation** – nurodo, ar įrašymo operacija skirta naujam failui, ar esamo failo kopijai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2369">**Data_IsNewFileCreation** - Indicates if the save operation is for a new file or a copy of an existing file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2370">**Data_IsSignedIn** – ar failo įrašymo metu vartotojas yra prisijungęs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2370">**Data_IsSignedIn** - Whether or not a user is signed in when the file is saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2371">**Data_SaveErrorCode** – skaitinė reikšmė, nustatoma įvykus klaidai, kad padėtų nustatyti klaidos tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2371">**Data_SaveErrorCode** - A numerical value that is set if there is an error to help identify the kind of error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2372">**Data_SaveErrorDomain** – nurodo SaveErrorCode domeną, kaip apibrėžta „Apple“ SaveErrorDomains – „yra pasirenkamos eilutės, skirtos kodų grupėms atskirti“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2372">**Data_SaveErrorDomain** - Specifies the domain of the SaveErrorCode as defined by Apple SaveErrorDomains "are arbitrary strings used to differentiate groups of codes".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2373">**Data_SaveLocation** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas, ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2373">**Data_SaveLocation** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2374">**Data_SaveOperationType** – skaitinė reikšmė, apibrėžta „Apple“ NSSaveOperationType reikšmių grupėje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2374">**Data_SaveOperationType** - A numerical value defined by Apple's NSSaveOperationType group of values.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_cloudupsellshown"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2375">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellShown</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2375">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellShown</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2376">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2376">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2377">Šis įvykis įrašo, kada vartotojas peržvelgia papildomo debesies srauto pardavimo dokumentą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2377">This event records when a user goes through the document upsell to cloud flow.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2378">Šie duomenys naudojami siekiant geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirčių prioritetus, susijusius su dokumentų perkėlimu į debesį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2378">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2379">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2379">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2380">**Data_FileStyle** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti, koks scenarijus buvo naudojamas papildomo pardavimo patirties rodymui, pvz., automatinio įrašymo jungiklio ar bendrinimo mygtuko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2380">**Data_FileStyle** - A numerical value that indicates from what scenario the upsell experience was shown like from an autosave toggle or a share button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2381">**Data_FileType** – pirmi keturi esamo failo plėtinio simboliai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2381">**Data_FileType** - The first four characters of the current file's extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2382">**Data_InDocStage** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar papildomo pardavimo patirtis rodoma iš dokumentų galerijos, ar dokumento lango.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2382">**Data_InDocStage** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience is shown from the Document Gallery or from within a document window.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2383">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar taip pat atidarytas esamas dokumentas, kuriame rodoma papildomo pardavimo patirtis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2383">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** - A Boolean that indicates if the current document for which the upsell experience is being shown is also open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2384">**Data_IsDraft** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar esamas failas kada nors buvo įrašytas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2384">**Data_IsDraft** - A Boolean that indicates if the current file has ever been saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2385">**Data_IsSheetModal** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar papildomo pardavimo patirtis buvo pateikta modališkai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2385">**Data_IsSheetModal** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience was presented modally or not.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_cloudupsellupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2386">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2386">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellUpload</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2387">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2387">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2388">Šis įvykis fiksuoja kada vartotojas pasirenka nusiųsti naują ar vietinį failą į debesį ir šios operacijos rezultatą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2388">This event records when a user chooses to upload a new or local file to the cloud and the result of that operation.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2389">Šie duomenys naudojami siekiant geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirčių prioritetus, susijusius su dokumentų perkėlimu į debesį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2389">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2390">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2390">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2391">**Data_FileStyle** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti, koks scenarijus buvo naudojamas papildomo pardavimo patirties rodymui, pavyzdžiui, automatinio įrašymo jungiklio ar bendrinimo mygtuko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2391">**Data_FileStyle** - A numerical value that indicates from what scenario the upsell experience was shown like an autosave toggle or a share button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2392">**Data_FileType** – pirmi keturi esamo failo plėtinio simboliai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2392">**Data_FileType** - The first four characters of the current file's extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2393">**Data_InDocStage** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar papildomo pardavimo patirtis rodoma iš dokumentų galerijos ar dokumento lango.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2393">**Data_InDocStage** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience is shown from the Document Gallery or from within a document window.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2394">**Data_IsDefaultServiceLocation** – Bulio logikos reikšmė, nurodanti, ar pasirinkta dokumento įkėlimo vieta yra numatytoji vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2394">**Data_IsDefaultServiceLocation** - A Boolean value that indicates if the selected location to upload the document to is the default location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2395">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar taip pat atidarytas esamas dokumentas, kuriame rodoma papildomo pardavimo patirtis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2395">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** - A Boolean that indicates if the current document for which the upsell experience is being shown is also open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2396">**Data_IsDraft** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar esamas failas kada nors buvo įrašytas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2396">**Data_IsDraft** - A Boolean that indicates if the current file has ever been saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2397">**Data_IsSheetModal** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar papildomo pardavimo patirtis buvo pateikta modališkai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2397">**Data_IsSheetModal** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience was presented modally or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2398">**Data_LocationServiceType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2398">**Data_LocationServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2399">**Data_UploadAction** – užprogramuota eilutė, nurodanti, ar nusiuntimas buvo perkėlimo, ar kopijavimo operacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2399">**Data_UploadAction** - A hard coded string that indicates whether the upload was a move or a copy operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2400">**Data_UploadResult** – užprogramuota eilutė, nurodanti mėginimo nusiųsti rezultatą, įskaitant (bet tuo neapsiribojant) parametrus „Success“, „UserCancelledUpload“ ir „PreAuthFailed“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2400">**Data_UploadResult** - A hard coded string that indicates the result of the attempt to upload including but not limited to ''Success", "UserCancelledUpload", and "PreAuthFailed".</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_copylinkoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2401">Office.Security.SecureReaderHost.OpenInOSR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2401">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CopyLinkOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2402">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2402">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2403">Šis įvykis fiksuoja, kada vartotojas pasirenka dokumento bendrinimą sugeneruodamas nuorodą į debesies dokumentą ir yra naudojamas norint geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirties prioritetus, atsižvelgiant į dokumentų bendrinimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2403">This event records when a user chooses to share a document by generating a link to a cloud document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2404">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2404">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2405">**Data_ServiceType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas, ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2405">**Data_ ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2406">**Data_LinkType** – užprogramuota eilutė, aprašanti kvietimo operacijos rūšį, pvz., „ViewOnly“ ir „ViewAndEdit“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2406">**Data_LinkType** - A hard coded string that describes the kind of invite operation performed like "ViewOnly" and "ViewAndEdit".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2407">**Data_ShareScenario** – užprogramuota eilutė, aprašanti, ar failas buvo bendrintas iš programos vartotojo sąsajos, įskaitant (bet tuo neapsiribojant) „FileMenu“, „OpenTabShareActionMenu“, „RecentTabShareActionMenu“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2407">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard-coded string description of where within the application's user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_docsuionedriveshare"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2408">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_DocsUIOneDriveShare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2408">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_DocsUIOneDriveShare</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2409">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2409">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2410">Šis įvykis fiksuoja, kada vartotojas pasirenka bendrinti debesies dokumentą naudodamas „OneDrive“ bendrinimo patirtį ir yra naudojamas norint geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirties prioritetus, atsižvelgiant į dokumentų bendrinimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2410">This event records when a user chooses to share a cloud document using the OneDrive sharing experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2411">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2411">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2412">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareError** – jei bendrinimo patirties metu įvyksta klaida, tai yra skaitinė reikšmė, padedanti nustatyti trikties priežastį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2412">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareError** - If the sharing experience experiences an error this is a numerical value to help identify the reason for the failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2413">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareGrantAccessResult** – Bulio logikos reikšmė. Kai yra teisinga, nurodo, kad sėkmingai įvykdyta paprasta bendrinimo operacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2413">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareGrantAccessResult** - A Boolean value that when true indicates that a lightweight sharing operation successfully completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2414">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareSuccessType** – sėkmingai užbaigus bendrinimo operaciją, tai yra skaitinė reikšmė, naudojama nustatyti atliktos bendrinimo operacijos tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2414">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareSuccessType** - When a share operation successfully completes this is a numerical value used to determine what kind of sharing operation was completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2415">**Data_WebViewInfoResult** – jei nepavyko įkelti vartotojo sąsajos, tai yra skaitinė reikšmė, padedanti nustatyti trikties priežastį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2415">**Data_WebViewInfoResult** - If the user interface fails to load this is a numerical value to help identify the reason for the failure.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2416">**Data_WebViewLoadTimeInMs** – skaitinė reikšmė, kuri registruoja laiką, reikalingą įkelti žiniatinklio vartotojo sąsają.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2416">**Data_WebViewLoadTimeInMs** - A numerical value that records the amount of time it took for the web user interface to load.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_invitepeople"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2417">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_InvitePeople</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2417">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_InvitePeople</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2418">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2418">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2419">Šis įvykis fiksuoja, kada vartotojas pasirenka žmonių kvietimą prisijungti prie debesies dokumento ir yra naudojamas norint geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirties prioritetus, atsižvelgiant į dokumentų bendrinimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2419">This event records when a user chooses to invite people to a cloud document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2420">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2420">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2421">**Data_ServiceType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2421">**Data_ ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2422">**Data_InviteeCount** – bendras kontaktų, pakviestų prisijungti prie dokumento atliekant vieną kvietimo veiksmą, skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2422">**Data_InviteeCount** - The total number of contacts invited to a document in one invite action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2423">**Data_LinkType** – užprogramuota eilutė, aprašanti kvietimo operacijos rūšį, pvz., „ViewOnly“ ir „ViewAndEdit“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2423">**Data_LinkType** - A hard-coded string that describes the kind of invite operation performed like "ViewOnly" and "ViewAndEdit".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2424">**Data_MessageLength** – bendras išsiųsto kvietimo pranešimo simbolių skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2424">**Data_MessageLength** - A numerical count of the total number of characters sent in the invite message.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2425">**Data_ShareScenario** – užprogramuota eilutė, aprašanti, ar failas buvo bendrintas iš programos vartotojo sąsajos, įskaitant (bet tuo neapsiribojant) „FileMenu“, „OpenTabShareActionMenu“, „RecentTabShareActionMenu“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2425">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard coded string description of where within the application's user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_sendacopyoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2426">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_SendACopyOperation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2426">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_SendACopyOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2427">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2427">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2428">Įvykis fiksuoja, kada vartotojas pasirenka siųsti dokumento kopiją ir yra naudojamas norint geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirties prioritetus, atsižvelgiant į dokumentų bendrinimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2428">The event records when a user chooses to send a copy of a document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2429">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2429">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2430">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** – Bulio logikos reikšmė, nurodanti, ar skirtukas Pagrindinis šiuo metu pasiekiamas vartotojui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2430">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the Home tab is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2431">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** – Bulio logikos reikšmė, nurodanti, ar patirtis Rekomenduojama šiuo metu pasiekiamas vartotojui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2431">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the "Recommended" experience is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2432">**Data_OperationType** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti vykdomos kopijos siuntimo operacijos tipą, pvz., siųsti kopiją el. paštu arba nusiųsti kopiją naudojantis „Apple“ bendrinimo valdymo funkcija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2432">**Data_OperationType** - A numerical value to indicate what kind of send a copy operation is taking place like sending a copy in an email or sending a copy through Apple's share control.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2433">**Data_ServiceType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2433">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2434">**Data_ShareFileType** – užprogramuotas eilutės aprašas, nurodantis bendrinamo objekto tipą, įskaitant (bet tuo neapsiribojant) „Dokumentas“, „PDF“, „Paveikslėlis“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2434">**Data_ShareFileType** - A hard coded string description of what type of object is being shared including but not limited to, "Document", "PDF", "Picture".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2435">**Data_ShareScenario** – užprogramuota eilutė, aprašanti, ar failas buvo bendrintas iš programos vartotojo sąsajos, įskaitant (bet tuo neapsiribojant) „FileMenu“, „OpenTabShareActionMenu“, „RecentTabShareActionMenu“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2435">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard coded string description of where within the application's user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2436">**Data_SharingService** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar failas buvo sukurtas, kai vartotojas ieškojo šablono.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2436">**Data_SharingService** - A Boolean that indicates whether the file was created when the user was searching for a template.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_upsellshare"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2437">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_UpsellShare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2437">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_UpsellShare</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2438">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2438">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2439">Šis įvykis įrašo, kai vartotojas peržvelgia papildomo debesies srauto pardavimo dokumentą, kai bando bendrinti dokumentą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2439">This event records when a user goes through the document upsell to cloud flow when trying to share a document.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2440">Šie duomenys naudojami, kad geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirčių prioritetus, susijusius su dokumentų perkėlimu į debesį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2440">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2441">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2441">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2442">**Data_FileOperationResult** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti, ar pavyko atlikti operaciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2442">**Data_FileOperationResult** - A numerical value to indicate whether the operation succeeded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2443">**Data_HostedFromDocStage** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar vartotojas peržiūri debesies srauto reklamą naudodami DocStage funkcijas arba iš atidaryto dokumento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2443">**Data_HostedFromDocStage** - A Boolean to indicate if a user is going through the upsell to cloud flow from the DocStage experience or from an open document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2444">**Data_isLocalCopyOn** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar naudoti pasirinko saugoti dokumento vietinę kopiją, kuri buvo nusiųsta į debesį arba perkelti esamą dokumentą į debesį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2444">**Data_isLocalCopyOn** - A Boolean to indicate if the use chose to keep a local copy of the document being uploaded to a cloud location or move the existing document to a cloud location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2445">**Data_NewFileType** – naujos failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2445">**Data_NewFileType** - An abstract categorization of the location of the new location of the file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2446">**Data_OriginalFileType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2446">**Data_OriginalFileType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2614">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2614">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

#### <a name="officefileiocsiccachedfilecsisavefilebasic"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2736">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiSaveFileBasic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2736">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiSaveFileBasic</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2737">Leidžia mums žinoti, ar failas iš FIO sluoksnio įrašytas sėkmingai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2737">Allows us to know if a file was successfully saved from the FIO Layer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2738">Naudojama funkcijos sveikatai užtikrinti ir stebėti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2738">Used for Feature Health and monitoring.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2739">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2739">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2740">**Activity.Group –** žymė, leidžianti nustatyti stebimų įvykių rinkinį, grupuojamą sėkmingam atlikimui valdyti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2740">**Activity.Group -** tag that allows a set of monitoring events to be grouped to manage overall success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2741">**Activity.IsHVA –** žyma, nurodanti, kad įvykis yra kritinis vartotojų sėkmingiems veiksmams užtikrinti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2741">**Activity.IsHVA -** flag to indicate that event is critical to user success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2742">**Data.AsyncOpen –** žyma, nurodanti, kad dokumentas buvo atidarytas su turiniu, gautu po pagrindinės dalies atidarymo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2742">**Data.AsyncOpen -** flag to indicate that the document was opened with content that arrived after the main body was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2743">**Data.BaseDownloadTriggered –** keičia sekimo diagnostiką, nurodančią, kad buvo užklausta pagrindinė dokumento versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2743">**Data.BaseDownloadTriggered -** Change tracking diagnostic indicating that the base version of the document was requested</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2744">**Data.BlockAutoUploadReasons –** užblokuotos nusiuntimo būsenos priežasčių kodai (pvz. automatinis įrašymas išjungtas, dokumentas perkeliamas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2744">**Data.BlockAutoUploadReasons -** Reason codes for blocked upload state (e.g. Autosave is turned off, the document is transitioning)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2745">**Data.BlockUploadDueToFailedSaveAsOverExisting –** nusiuntimas užblokuotas, nes kartojant jis nepavyks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2745">**Data.BlockUploadDueToFailedSaveAsOverExisting -** Upload is blocked as it would fail if retried</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2746">**Data.CacheFileId –** prisijungia prie „Office“ dokumentų talpyklos telemetrijos, kad atliktų vartotojo patiriamų talpyklos problemų analizę</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2746">**Data.CacheFileId -** connects to Office Document Cache telemetry to enable impact analysis of cache issues on the user experience</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2747">**Data.ChartType –** nebenaudojamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2747">**Data.ChartType -** Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2748">**Data.CoAuthStatus –** informuoja apie dokumento bendradarbiavimo būseną įrašant</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2748">**Data.CoAuthStatus -** reports collaborative status of the document on Save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2749">**Data.CoauthUpdatesContext –** pranešamas kontekstas (suliejimas / laipsniškas atidarymas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2749">**Data.CoauthUpdatesContext -** reports context (Merge/Incremental Open)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2750">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload –** kelionių į serverį ir atgal skaičius, naudotas veikimo triktims ir tinklo problemoms šalinti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2750">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2751">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsUpload –** kelionių į serverį ir atgal skaičius, naudotas našumo triktims ir tinklo problemoms šalinti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2751">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsUpload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2759">**Data.Doc.AsyncOpenKind** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2759">**Data.Doc.AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

#### <a name="officefindtimeappfailedtostart"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2883">Office.FindTime.AppFailedToStart</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2883">Office.FindTime.AppFailedToStart</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2884">Surinkta, kai taikomoji programa nepasileidžia dėl netikėtos klaidos paleidimo metu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2884">Collected when app fails to start due to an unexpected error during startup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2885">Naudojama sekti išimtis ir gedimus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2885">Used to track exceptions & crashes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2886">Padeda stebėti ir derinti taikomosios programos sveikatą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2886">Helps monitor & debug app health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2887">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2887">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2888">**DateTime** – laiko žyma, kada įvykis užregistruotas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2888">**DateTime** - Timestamp of when the event is logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2889">**EventName** – užregistruoto įvykio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2889">**EventName** - The name of the event being logged</span></span>

#### <a name="office_firstrun_apple_activationresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2890">Office_FirstRun_Apple_ActivationResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2890">Office_FirstRun_Apple_ActivationResult</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2891">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2891">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2892">Įvykis naudojamas mūsų taikomosios programos aktyvinimo srauto sveikatai stebėti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2892">The event is used to monitor the health of our application activation flow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2893">Renkame duomenis, kad išsiaiškintume „Office 365“ prenumeratos aktyvinimo rezultatus kartu su aktyvinimui naudojamu srautu (pirmojo sistemos paleidimo programa (FRE), srautas taikomojoje programoje, pirkimas ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2893">We collect data to figure out the outcome of the Office 365 subscription activation along with the flow used to activate (First Run Experience, In-App-Flow, Purchase, etc.).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2894">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2894">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2895">**Data_ActivationStatusCollectionTime** – laiko žyma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2895">**Data_ActivationStatusCollectionTime** – A timestamp</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2896">**Data_ActivationStatusError** – aktyvinimo klaidos kodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2896">**Data_ActivationStatusError** – An activation error code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2897">**Data_ActivationStatusFlowType** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti aktyvinimo srauto tipą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2897">**Data_ActivationStatusFlowType** – A numeric value indicating the type of activation flow</span></span>

#### <a name="office_firstrun_apple_activationstatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2898">Office_FirstRun_Apple_ActivationStatus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2898">Office_FirstRun_Apple_ActivationStatus</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2899">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2899">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2900">Įvykis naudojamas išsiaiškinti „Office 365“ prenumeratos aktyvinimo rezultatus kartu su aktyvinimui naudojamu srautu (pirmojo sistemos paleidimo programa, srautas taikomojoje programoje, pirkimas ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2900">The event is used to figure out the outcome of the Office 365 subscription activation along with the flow used to activate (FRE, InApp, Purchase, etc.).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2901">Renkame duomenis, kuriuose yra aktyvinimo tipas, srauto tipas (FRE/DocStage/pirkimas) ir „Office“ licencijavimo tarnybos ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2901">We collect data containing the Activation type, flow type (FRE/DocStage/Purchase) and Office Licensing Service ID.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2902">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2902">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2903">**Data_ActivationTypeCollectionTime** – laiko žyma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2903">**Data_ActivationTypeCollectionTime** – A timestamp</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2904">**Data_ActivationTypeFlowType** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti aktyvinimo srauto tipą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2904">**Data_ActivationTypeFlowType** – A numeric value indicating the type of activation flow</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2905">**Data_ActivationTypeOLSLicense** – licencijos identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2905">**Data_ActivationTypeOLSLicense** – An identifier of the License</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2906">**Data_ActivationTypeStatus** – aktyvinimo būsenos kodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2906">**Data_ActivationTypeStatus** – An activation status code.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_firstrun_apple_firstruncomplete"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2907">Office_FirstRun_Apple_FirstRunComplete</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2907">Office_FirstRun_Apple_FirstRunComplete</span></span>

#### <a name="office_firstrun_apple_inapprestoreattempted"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2988">Office_FirstRun_Apple_InAppRestoreAttempted</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2988">Office_FirstRun_Apple_InAppRestoreAttempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2993">**Data_EventId** – kodas, nurodantis bandymo rezultato tipą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2993">**Data_EventId** - A code denoting the type of outcome of the attempt</span></span>

#### <a name="office_firstrun_apple_inapprestoreattemptfailed"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2995">Office_FirstRun_Apple_InAppRestoreAttemptFailed</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2995">Office_FirstRun_Apple_InAppRestoreAttemptFailed</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2996">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2996">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2997">Įvykis naudojamas mūsų taikomosios programos pirkimo programėlėje srauto sveikatai stebėti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2997">The event is used to monitor the health of our application in-app purchase flow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2998">Renkame duomenis, kad galėtume stebėti kortelėje atliekamą atkūrimą ir susieti srautą bei klaidas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2998">We collect data to track the attempted In-App restorations and their associated flows and errors.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-2999">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-2999">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3000">**Data_RestoreButtonFlowType** – kodas, nurodantis vykdyto vartotojo srauto tipą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3000">**Data_RestoreButtonFlowType** - A code denoting the type of user flow that was exercised</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3001">**Data_RestoredFailedPaymentCancelledFlowType** – kodas, nurodantis vykdyto mokėjimo atšaukimo srauto tipą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3001">**Data_RestoredFailedPaymentCancelledFlowType** - A code denoting the type of payment cancellation flow that was exercised</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3003">**Data_RestoredFailedUnKnownResult** – ar bandymas nepavyko dėl nežinomų priežasčių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3003">**Data_RestoredFailedUnKnownResult** - Whether the attempt failed due to unknown reasons</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3005">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3005">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3006">Įvykis leidžia mums žinoti, kad vartotojas atliko iki galo pirmojo sistemos paleidimo programą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3006">The event lets us know a user has gone thru first run experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3007">Šį įvykį naudojame norėdami išsiaiškinti, ar pirmojo sistemos paleidimo programa (FRE) sėkmingai užbaigta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3007">We use this event to figure out if the First Run-Experience (FRE) was completed successfully.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3009">**Data_FirstRunCollectionTime** – laiko žyma, skirta srauto užbaigimo laikui registruoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3009">**Data_FirstRunCollectionTime** - A timestamp registering the time at which the flow was completed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3011">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3011">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3012">Įvykis leidžia mums žinoti, kad vartotojas paleido pirmojo sistemos paleidimo programą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3012">The event lets us know a user has entered first run experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3013">Šį įvykį naudojame išsiaiškinti, ar pirmojo sistemos paleidimo programa (FRE) buvo sėkmingai paleista.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3013">We use this event to figure out if the First Run-Experience (FRE) was started successfully.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3044">**cardCorrelationId** pirmiau esančio Data.appContextId dublikatas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3044">**cardCorrelationId** - Duplicate of Data.appContextId above</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3046">**ClientTimeStamp** – laikas programoje, kada buvo užregistruotas įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3046">**ClientTimeStamp** - Time on the application when the event was logged</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3047">**consumerCorrelationId** pirmiau esančio Data.clientCorrelationId dublikatas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3047">**consumerCorrelationId** - Duplicate of Data.clientCorrelationId above</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3048">**externalAppSessionCorrelationId** – programos visuotinis unikalusis identifikatorius, skirtas identifikuoti visas asmenines korteles, atidarytas to paties antrinio seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3048">**externalAppSessionCorrelationId** - A globally unique identifier for the app to identify all persona cards opened in the same sub-session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3049">**Data.region** – profilio kortelės vidinės tarnybos, prie kurios vartotojas yra prisijungęs, geografinis regionas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3049">**Data.region** -The geographical region of the profile card backend service to which user is connected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3054">**Data.UserInfo.Id** – įmonės „Microsoft“ paskyros visuotinis unikalusis vartotojo identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3054">**Data.UserInfo.Id** - The globally unique user identifier for an enterprise Microsoft account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3055">**Data.UserInfo.MsaId** – vartotojo „Microsoft“ paskyros visuotinis unikalusis vartotojo identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3055">**Data.UserInfo.MsaId** - The globally unique user identifier for a consumer Microsoft account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3056">**Data.UserInfo.OMSTenantId** – nuomotojas, su kuriuo yra susieta vartotojo prenumerata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3056">**Data.UserInfo.OMSTenantId** - The tenant that a user's subscription is tied to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3057">Leidžia mums klasifikuoti problemas ir nustatyti, ar problema yra plačiai paplitusi, ar izoliuota atskirų nuomotojų grupėje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3057">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users or a specific tenant</span></span>

    - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3219">**networkEffectiveType** – tinklo ryšio efektyvus tipas, pvz., slow-2g Online, skirtas identifikuoti, ar vartotojas yra prisijungęs prie interneto asmeninės kortelės rodymo metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3219">**networkEffectiveType** - The effective type of network connection, e.g. "slow-2g Online" to identify whether the user is connected to the internet at the time of showing the persona card</span></span>
