#### <a name="office_officemobile_pdfviewer_pdffileopenmeasurements"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3249">Office_OfficeMobile_PdfViewer_PdfFileOpenMeasurements</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3249">Office_OfficeMobile_PdfViewer_PdfFileOpenMeasurements</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3250">Šis įvykis renkamas „Union iOS“, jis fiksuoja, kada failas atidaromas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3250">This event is collected for Union iOS, it records when a file open operation takes place.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3251">Mes renkame šiuos duomenis, kad būtų užtikrintas tinkamas visų failų, esančių programoje, atidarymas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3251">We collect this data to ensure good performance for all file opens on the app.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3252">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3252">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3253">**"Data_Doc_ActivationFQDN** – teikėjo taikomosios programos, skirtos failo suaktyvinimo scenarijui, domeno vardas (registruojama tik 1-osios šalies taikomosios programos informacija).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3253">**Data_Doc_ActivationFQDN** - Domain name of the Provider app for a file activation scenario (only 1st party app info is being logged).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3254">**Data_Doc_DownloadDurationms** – laikas, per kurį atsisiunčiamas PDF debesies failas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3254">**Data_Doc_DownloadDurationms** - Time to download a PDF cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3255">**Data_Doc_DownloadEndTime** – debesies failo atsisiuntimo pabaigos laiko žyma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3255">**Data_Doc_DownloadEndTime** - Timestamp for end of download of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3256">**Data_Doc_DownloadEndTime** – debesies failo atsisiuntimo pradžios laiko žyma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3256">**Data_Doc_DownloadStartTime** – Timestamp for start of download of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3257">**Data_Doc_FileOpSessionID** – dokumento seanso unikalusis ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3257">**Data_Doc_FileOpSessionID** - Unique Id for a Document Session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3258">**Data_Doc_Location** – vieta, kurioje yra failas (vietinis, ODSP, „iCloud“, trečiosios šalies failų programa, „wopi“).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3258">**Data_Doc_Location** - Location where the file sits (Local, ODSP, iCloud, third party files app , wopi</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3259">**Data_Doc_OpenCompletionTime** – PDF failo atidarymo operacijos pabaigos laiko žyma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3259">**Data_Doc_OpenCompletionTime** - Timestamp for end of open operation of a PDF file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3260">**Data_Doc_OpenDurationms** – laikas milisekundėmis, per kurį atidaromas PDF failas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3260">**Data_Doc_OpenDurationms** - Time to open a PDF file in milliseconds.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3261">**Data_Doc_OpenStartTime** – PDF failo atidarymo operacijos pradžios laiko žyma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3261">**Data_Doc_OpenStartTime** - Timestamp for start of open operation of a PDF file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3262">**Data_Doc_TelemetryReason** – telemetrijos priežastys įvykiui atidaryti (pvz., atidarymas iš MRU arba naršymas, failo suaktyvinimas, protokolo suaktyvinimas ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3262">**Data_Doc_TelemetryReason** - Telemetry reason for the open event (eg: open from MRU or browse, File Activation, Protocol Activation, etc.).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3263">**Doc_RenderDurationms**– laikas, per kurį sugeneruojamas PDF failas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3263">**Doc_RenderDurationms** - Time to render a pdf file</span></span>


#### <a name="office_officemobile_pdfviewer_pdffileoperations"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3264">Office_OfficeMobile_PdfViewer_PdfFileOperations</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3264">Office_OfficeMobile_PdfViewer_PdfFileOperations</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3265">Įvykis renkamas naudojantis „Office“ programa, skirta „Android“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3265">The event is collected for the Office app for Android.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3266">Jis įrašomas, kai vykdoma PDF failo atidarymo, uždarymo arba įrašymo operacija, ir naudojamas siekiant suprasti ir nustatyti prioritetus vartotojo patirčiai pagal PDF failo operacijos informaciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3266">It records when a PDF open, close, or save operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize the user experience based on PDF file operation information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3267">Įvykis mums leidžia užtikrinti, kad PDF failų atidarymo, uždarymo ir įrašymo operacijos būtų vykdomos, kaip numatyta, ir pagerinti PDF failų operacijų veikimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3267">The event enables us to keep the PDF open, close and save operations performing as expected, and to improve PDF file operation performance.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3268">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3268">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3269">**Data_Doc_FileOpSessionID** – dokumento seanso unikalusis ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3269">**Data_Doc_FileOpSessionID** - Unique ID for a Document Session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3270">**Data_ErrorCode** – klaida, rodoma failo atidarymo trikčių / atsisiuntimo trikčių / atsisiuntimo atšaukimo atveju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3270">**Data_ErrorCode** - error in case of file open failures/download failures / download canceled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3271">**Data_ErrorMessage** – pranešimas, susijęs su klaidos kodu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3271">**Data_ErrorMessage** - relevant message-to-error code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3272">**Data_FailureReason** – esant atidarymo trikčiai, nurodoma trikties priežastis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3272">**Data_FailureReason** - In case of open failure, these enums define the reason for failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3273">**Data_FileLocation** – failo vieta, pvz., „Local“, „ODSP“, „iCloud“ ir pan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3273">**Data_FileLocation** - Location where the file sits, ex: Local, ODSP, iCloud, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3274">**Data_FileOpenEntryPoint** – failo atidarymo įvesties taškas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3274">**Data_FileOpenEntryPoint** - entry point for file open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3275">**Data_FileSize** – failo, su kuriuo vykdoma operacija, dydis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3275">**Data_FileSize** - Size of the file on which the operation is happening</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3276">**Data_OpenMode** – kokiu režimu buvo atidarytas PDF failas, pvz., 0: peržiūros režimas, 2: pasirašymo režimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3276">**Data_OpenMode** - In which mode the PDF was opened, ex: 0: View mode, 2: Sign mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3277">**Data_PageCount** – puslapių skaičius PDF faile.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3277">**Data_PageCount** - Count of page in the PDF File.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3278">**Data_PasswordProtected** – žyma, kuri nurodo, ar failas apsaugotas slaptažodžiu, ar ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3278">**Data_PasswordProtected** - Marker that tell whether the file is password protected or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3279">**Data_ProviderApp** – dabartinė teikėjo programa tik failo aktyvinimo atveju </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3279">**Data_ProviderApp** - currently providing provider app in case of file activation only</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3280">**Data_ReadOnly** – žyma, kuri nurodo, ar failas yra tik skaitomas, ar ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3280">**Data_ReadOnly** - Marker that tell whether the file is read-only or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3281">**Data_Result** – vykdomos operacijos būsena, pvz., teisinga: pavyko, neteisinga: triktis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3281">**Data_Result** - The status of the operation being performed, ex: true:success, false:failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3282">**Data_Type** – failo operacijos tipas (atidarymas, uždarymas arba įrašymas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3282">**Data_Type** - Type of file operation (open, close or save)</span></span> 

#### <a name="officeonenoteandroidappnavigationnavigationuistatechanged-onenoteappnavigationnavigationuistatechanged-previous-name"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3283">Office.OneNote.Android.App.Navigation.NavigationUIStateChanged, OneNote.App.Navigation.NavigationUIStateChanged *(ankstesnis pavadinimas)*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3283">Office.OneNote.Android.App.Navigation.NavigationUIStateChanged, OneNote.App.Navigation.NavigationUIStateChanged *(previous name)*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3284">Šis įvykis renka kritinį signalą, naudojamą užtikrinti, kad „OneNote“ vartotojai galėtų sėkmingai naršyti programoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3284">This event collects the critical signal used to ensure OneNote users can successfully navigate through the app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3285">Telemetrija naudojama siekiant užtikrinti regresijos aptikimą, kuris ypač svarbus programai „OneNote“ ir tarnybos sveikatai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3285">The telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3286">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3286">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3287">**IS_SPANNED** – nurodo, ar programa veikia segmentuotu režimu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3287">**IS_SPANNED** - Indicates whether the app is in a spanned mode.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3288">Registruojama konkrečiai sulenkiamų įrenginių atveju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3288">This is specifically logged for foldable devices.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3289">**NEW_STATE** – nurodo programų būseną iškart po naršymo veiksmo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3289">**NEW_STATE** - Indicates the applications' state right after the navigation</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenoteandroidlenssdkofficelenslaunched-onenotelenssdkofficelenslaunched-previous-name"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3291">Office.OneNote.Android.LensSDK.OfficeLensLaunched, OneNote.LensSDK.OfficeLensLaunched *(ankstesnis pavadinimas)*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3291">Office.OneNote.Android.LensSDK.OfficeLensLaunched, OneNote.LensSDK.OfficeLensLaunched *(previous name)*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3292">Šis įvykis renka kritinį signalą, naudojamą siekiant užtikrinti sėkmingą „OfficeLens“ paleidimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3292">This event collects the critical signal used to ensure that OfficeLens is launched correctly.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3293">Telemetrija naudojama siekiant užtikrinti regresijos aptikimą, kuris ypač svarbus programai „OneNote“ ir tarnybos sveikatai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3293">The telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3294">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3294">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3295">**CAPTURE_MODE** – nurodo, kokiu režimu buvo paleista „OfficeLens“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3295">**CAPTURE_MODE** - Indicates which mode has OfficeLens been launched in.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3296">Jis gali būti numatytasis, redagavimo, greitojo įterpimo arba vaizdo įrašo importavimo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3296">It could be default, edit, fast insert or video import.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3297">**ERROR_CODE** – nurodo paleidimo klaidos kodą, jei paleidžiant įvyko klaida.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3297">**ERROR_CODE** - Indicates the launch error code in case there was an error while launching.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3298">**IMAGE_COUNT** – nurodo padarytų nuotraukų skaičių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3298">**IMAGE_COUNT** - Indicates the number of images taken</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3299">**LAUNCH_REASON** – nurodo „OfficeLens“ paleidimo procesą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3299">**LAUNCH_REASON** - Indicates the flow under which OfficeLens was launched.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3300">Tai gali būti atlikta užrakto ekrane arba per fotoaparato ar galerijos parinktis, priklijuojamuose lapeliuose arba „OneNote“ drobėje ir pan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3300">It could be over the lock screen or via Camera or Gallery options in StickyNotes or via OneNote Canvas etc.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenotecanvasinkinkstrokelogger"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3301">Office.OneNote.Canvas.Ink.InkStrokeLogger</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3301">Office.OneNote.Canvas.Ink.InkStrokeLogger</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3302">Šis įvykis naudojamas aptikti ir diagnozuoti aukšto dažnio klaidą, su kuria vartotojas susiduria naudodamas rankraščio funkciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3302">This event is used to detect and diagnose a high frequency bug that a user encounters while using Ink feature.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3303">Tai bus panaudota norint nustatyti tinkamiausią šios problemos nustatymo būdą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3303">This will be used to determine the most appropriate mode of fixing this issue.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3304">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3304">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3305">**CurrentCanvasZoomFactor** – dabartinis drobės padidinimo koeficientas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3305">**CurrentCanvasZoomFactor** - Current Zoom factor of the canvas.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3306">**CurrentNotebook** – dabartinio aktyvaus bloknoto identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3306">**CurrentNotebook** - Identifier of the current active notebook.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3307">**CurrentPage** – dabartinio aktyvaus puslapio identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3307">**CurrentPage** - Identifier of the current active page</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3308">**CurrentSection** – dabartinio aktyvaus skyriaus identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3308">**CurrentSection** - Identifier of the current active section.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3309">**DefaultCanvasZoomFactor** – drobės padidinimo koeficiento numatytoji reikšmė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3309">**DefaultCanvasZoomFactor** - Default Zoom factor of the canvas.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3310">**InkStrokeCount** – bendras rankraščio brūkštelėjimų skaičius nuo paskutinio įrašo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3310">**InkStrokeCount** - Total count of ink strokes since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3311">**InkStrokeWithLayerInkEffect** – rankraščio brūkštelėjimų su sluoksnio rankraščio efektu skaičius nuo paskutinio įrašo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3311">**InkStrokeWithLayerInkEffect** - Count of ink strokes with layer ink effect since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3312">**InkStrokeWithoutPressureCount** – nespaudžiamų rankraščio brūkštelėjimų skaičius nuo paskutinio įrašo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3312">**InkStrokeWithoutPressureCount** - Count of Ink Strokes without Pressure since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3313">**InkStrokeWithPencilInkEffect** – rankraščio brūkštelėjimų su pieštuku skaičius nuo paskutinio įrašo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3313">**InkStrokeWithPencilInkEffect** - Count of ink strokes with pencil ink effect since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3314">**InkStrokeWithTilt** – rankraščio brūkštelėjimų su pakreipimu skaičius nuo paskutinio įrašo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3314">**InkStrokeWithTilt** - Count of ink strokes with tilt since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3322">**IsRecentsView** – nurodo, ar puslapis sukuriamas iš Naujausių, ar ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3322">**IsRecentsView** - Indicates whether a page is created from a recents or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3323">**NavView** – nurodo, ar puslapis sukuriamas iš naršymo rodinio, ar ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3323">**NavView** - Indicates whether a page is created from a navigation view or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3324">**NoteType** – nurodo puslapio tipą (sparčioji pastaba, sąrašas arba nuotrauka).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3324">**NoteType** - Indicates the type (quick note, list, or photo) of a page.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3326">**RailState** – nurodo „OneNote“ naršymo kreiptuvo būseną kuriant puslapį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3326">**RailState** - Indicates the state of OneNote's navigation rail when creating a page.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3327">**Trigger** – nurodo įvesties tašką, kuriame pradedamas puslapio kūrimo veiksmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3327">**Trigger** - Indicates an entry point where the create page action is started.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenotestickynotesnotecreated-on-ios-onenotestickynotesnotecreated-on-android"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3383">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated („iOS“), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated („Android“)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3383">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (on iOS), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (on Android)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3384">Tai kritinis signalas, naudojamas stebėti priklijuojamų lapelių galimybę kurti pastabas programoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3384">This is a critical signal that is used to monitor the ability of Sticky Notes users to create notes in the app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3385">Telemetrija naudojama siekiant užtikrinti regresijos aptikimą, kuris ypač svarbus programai „OneNote“ ir tarnybos sveikatai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3385">Telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3386">Jei vartotojai negali sukurti pastabos, suaktyvinamas didelės svarbos incidentas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3386">If users can't create a note, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3387">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3387">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3388">**NoteLocalId** – atskiriamas unikalusis identifikatorius, priskirtas pastabai tuo metu, kai vartotojas sukuria pastabą programoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3388">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time of a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3389">**IsExportable** – žymė, nurodanti, ar šis įvykis tapo vartotojo veiksmo rezultatu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3389">**IsExportable** - A flag indicating whether this event was a result of a user action or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3390">Turėtų būti nustatyta į True, nes NoteCreated yra vartotojo suaktyvinamas veiksmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3390">Should be set to True as NoteCreated is a user-triggered action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3391">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** – versijos numeris, nurodantis priklijuojamų lapelių programos, kurią naudoja vartotojas, versiją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3391">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3392">Leidžia mums nustatyti kurios produkto versijos rodo problemą, kad galėtume tinkamai nustatyti jos prioritetą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3392">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3397">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3397">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3398">**HasImages** – žymė, nurodanti, ar peržiūrėta pastaba turi joje išsaugotų vaizdų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3398">**HasImages** - A flag indicating whether the note viewed has images stored in it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3399">**IsExportable** – žymė, nurodanti, ar šis įvykis tapo vartotojo veiksmo rezultatu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3399">**IsExportable** - A flag indicating whether this event was a result of a user action or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3400">Turėtų būti nustatyta į True, nes NoteViewed yra vartotojo suaktyvinamas veiksmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3400">Should be set to True as NoteViewed is a user-triggered action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3401">**NoteLocalId** – atskiriamas unikalusis identifikatorius, priskirtas pastabai tuo metu, kai vartotojas sukuria pastabą programoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3401">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3402">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** – versijos numeris, nurodantis priklijuojamų lapelių programos, kurią naudoja vartotojas, versiją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3402">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3403">Leidžia mums nustatyti kurios produkto versijos rodo problemą, kad galėtume tinkamai nustatyti jos prioritetą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3403">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3405">Šis įvykis registruoja bloknoto sinchronizavimo rezultatą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3405">This event logs notebook sync result.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3406">Jis naudojamas norint suprasti, kiek reikia unikalių sinchronizavimo tikslų, apskaičiuojant „OneNote“ sinchronizavimo balą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3406">It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3409">**CachedError_Description** – talpyklinės klaidos aprašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3409">**CachedError_Description** -a description of the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3410">**CachedError_Tag** – nurodo, kur kode įvyksta talpyklinė klaida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3410">**CachedError_Tag** -indicate where in the code throws the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3411">**CachedError_Type** – talpyklinės klaidos tipas, pvz., „Win32Error“ ir t. t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3411">**CachedError_Type** -the type of the cached error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3412">**ExecutionTime** – laikas milisekundėmis, reikalingas bloknotui dubliuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3412">**ExecutionTime** -time in milliseconds taken to replicate the notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3413">**Gosid** – visuotinio objekto srities ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3413">**Gosid** -global object space ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3414">**IdentityType** – tapatybės tipas, pavyzdžiui, „Windows Live“, organizacijos ID ir t. t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3414">**IdentityType** -identity type, e.g. Windows Live, Org ID, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3418">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** – nurodo, ar talpyklinė klaida netikėta, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3418">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** -is the cached error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3419">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – nurodo, ar bloknoto lygio sinchronizavimo klaida suglaudinta, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3419">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** -is the notebook level sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3420">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – nurodo, ar bloknoto lygio sinchronizavimo klaida netikėta, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3420">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** -is the notebook level sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3421">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – nurodo, ar sekcijos sinchronizavimo klaida suglaudinta, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3421">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** -is the section sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3423">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** – nurodo, ar bloknotas sinchronizuotas naudojant šiuolaikinį puslapio turinio sinchronizavimą, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3423">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** -is the notebook sync using modern page content sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3424">**LastAttemptedSync** – laiko žyma, nurodanti, kada bloknotas buvo bandytas sinchronizuoti paskutinį kartą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3424">**LastAttemptedSync** -timestamp when the notebook was attempted to be synced last time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3427">**LastSuccessfulSync** – laiko žyma, nurodanti, kada bloknotas buvo sėkmingai sinchronizuotas prieš tai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3427">**LastSuccessfulSync** -timestamp when the notebook successfully synced before</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3429">**NotebookErrorCode** – nurodo, kad bloknoto lygio sinchronizavimo klaidos kodas įrašytas bloknoto diagramos srityje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3429">**NotebookErrorCode** -notebook level sync error code saved on notebook graph space</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3430">**NotebookId** – bloknoto ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3430">**NotebookId** -notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3431">**NotebookType** – bloknoto tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3431">**NotebookType** -notebook type</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3531">Surinkta uždarius „PowerPoint“ pateiktis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3531">Collected when PowerPoint presentations are closed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3532">Joje yra informacija, reikalinga tinkamai nustatyti ir diagnozuoti problemas, įvykusias uždarymo proceso metu, ir kurios yra vartotojo duomenų išlaikymo ir sinchronizavimo ribojimo priežastimi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3532">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen through the close process which entail persisting and syncing the user's data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3533">„Microsoft“ naudoja šiuos duomenis, kad užtikrintų, jog uždarymas veikia kaip priklauso ir vartotojo turinys yra sėkmingai išlaikomas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3533">Microsoft uses this data to ensure that close is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3534">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3534">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3535">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long –** ar šis žurnalo įrašas turi visą reikiamą dokumento telemetriją (Data\_Doc\_\* laukus)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3535">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3536">Jei ne, kodėl?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3536">If not, why?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3537">**Data\_AutoSaveDisabledReasons:string –** iš anksto nustatytų reikšmių, nurodančių kodėl šiame dokumente buvo išjungtas automatinis įrašymas, rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3537">**Data\_AutoSaveDisabledReasons:string -** Predefined set of values of why was autosave disabled on this document?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3538">(Suliejomo klaida, įrašymo klaida, grupės strategija ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3538">(Merge error, Save error, Group policy etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3539">**Data\_CloseReason:long –** kaip buvo vykdomas uždarymas?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3539">**Data\_CloseReason:long -** How was close performed?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3540">Uždarant dokumentą?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3540">Closing document?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3541">Uždarant programą?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3541">Closing app?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3542">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long –** neapdorojamų išimčių skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3542">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long -** Number of unhandled exceptions</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3543">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long –** veiklos atskyrimo / neveikimo trukmė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3543">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3544">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long –** kaip šis dokumentas buvo atidarytas (tik skaityti | skaityti ir rašyti)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3544">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3545">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long –** iš anksto apibrėžtų reikšmių, nurodančių dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežastis, rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3545">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3546">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3546">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3547">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long –** kaip dokumentas saugomas programoje „SharePoint“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3547">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3548">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long –** dokumento įmonės duomenų apsaugos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3548">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3549">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string –** dokumento plėtinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3549">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3550">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string –** dokumento plėtinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3550">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3551">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long –** iš anksto nustatytų failo formato reikšmių rinkinys (detalesnis nei plėtinio)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3551">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3552">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string –** vieta, kurioje saugomas dokumentas (SharePoint.com, live.net) galima tik „Office 365“ domenams</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3552">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3553">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string –** dokumento saugojimo vietos maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3553">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string -** Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3554">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string –** unikalus vartotojo GUID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3554">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string -** Unique GUID of user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3555">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string –** unikalus tapatybės identifikatorius, naudojamas veiksmui su bendrinamais dokumentais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3555">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3556">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long –** šablonas įvairiems pateikto dokumento IO, susietiems su žymėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3556">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long -** Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3557">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long –** iš anksto nustatytų reikšmių, nurodančių kokio tipo informacijos teisių valdymas taikomas šiam dokumentui, rinkinys (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3557">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3558">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool –** „true“, jeigu HTTP antraštė „IsCloudCollabEnabled“jau buvo gauta iš PARINKČIŲ užklausos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3558">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool -** True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3559">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool –** ar dokumentas buvo atidarytas palaipsniui (nauja funkcija, kuri atidaro dokumentą be būtinybės atsisiųsti visą dokumentą)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3559">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool -** Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3561">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool –** tikrina, ar dokumentas atidarytas iš vietinės talpyklos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3561">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool -** verifies if document is being opened from local cache</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3562">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool –** tikrina, ar dokumentas atidarytas iš aplanko, naudojamo „OneDrive“ taikomosios programos sinchronizavimo atsarginei kopijai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3562">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool -** verifies if document is being opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3567">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long –** iš anksto apibrėžtų dokumento žymėjimo tik skaityti reikšmių rinkinys (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3567">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why this document was marked read only (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3569">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – nurodo, kaip buvo nustatytas realaus laiko kanalas (RTC) dabartiniam failui (išjungtas, nepalaikomas, pagal pageidavimą, visada įjungta, ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3569">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3572">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long –** iš anksto apibrėžtų serverio tipo reikšmių rinkinys („SharePoint“, „DropBox“ ar WOPI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3572">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long -** Predefined set of values of type of server (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3574">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long –** generuotas GUID, identifikuojantis dokumento egzempliorių to paties proceso seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3574">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long -** generated GUID that Identifies the instance of the document within the same process session</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationnewdocument"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3601">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.NewDocument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3601">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.NewDocument</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3602">Surinkta, „PowerPoint“ naujos pateikties sukūrimo metu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3602">Collected when PowerPoint creates a new presentation.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3603"> Apima sėkmingą klaidos šalinimą ir našumo metrikas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3603"> Includes success failure and performance metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3604">Ši informacija naudojama užtikrinti, kad galime sukurti failus sėkmingai, nemažinant našumo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3604">This information is used to ensure we can create files successfully and with no degradation in performance.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3605">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3605">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3606">**NewDocumentType** – ar naujas dokumentas sukurtas naudojant šabloną, ar sukurtas tik tuščias dokumentas?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3606">**NewDocumentType** – Whether new document is created from template or just created blank?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3607">**FLifeguarded** – dokumento apsauga (funkcija, atkurianti sugadintos būsenos dokumentą nepateikdami raginimo vartotojui)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3607">**FLifeguarded** – Is document life guarded (feature that restores corrupt document state without prompting user)</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationopencompleteprotocol"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3608">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.OpenCompleteProtocol</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3608">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.OpenCompleteProtocol</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3609">Surinkta „PowerPoint“ atidarius pateiktis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3609">Collected when PowerPoint opens presentations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3610">Joje yra informacija, reikalinga tinkamai nustatyti ir diagnozuoti problemas, įvykusias atidarymo proceso baigiamosiose stadijose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3610">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen through the end stages of the open process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3611">„Microsoft“ naudoja šiuos duomenis užtikrinti, jog funkcija veikia kaip numatyta ir pateikčių atidarymas nesuprastėjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3611">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and there is no degradation to opening presentations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3612">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3612">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3613">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod:long –** iš anksto apibrėžtas antivirusinės programos nuskaitymo tipo reikšmių rinkinys (IOAV, AMSI, None ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3613">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod:long -** Predefined set of values of type of AntiVirus scanned (IOAV, AMSI, None etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3614">**Data\_AntiVirusScanStatus:long –** iš anksto apibrėžtas antivirusinės programos nuskaitymo, atliekamo atidarant kiekvieną dokumentą, reikšmių rinkinys (NoThreatsDetected, Failed, MalwareDetected ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3614">**Data\_AntiVirusScanStatus:long -** Predefined set of values of anti-virus scan that happens for every document opened (NoThreatsDetected, Failed, MalwareDetected etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3615">**Data\_CloseAndReopen:bool –** ar šis dokumentas buvo uždarytas, ar pakartotinai atidarytas?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3615">**Data\_CloseAndReopen:bool -** Was this document closed and reopened?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3616">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long –** veiklos atskyrimo / neveikimo trukmė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3616">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3617">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long –** kaip šis dokumentas buvo atidarytas (tik skaityti | skaityti ir rašyti)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3617">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3618">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long –** iš anksto apibrėžtų reikšmių, nurodančių dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežastis, rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3618">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3619">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3619">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3620">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long –** kaip dokumentas saugomas programoje „SharePoint“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3620">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3621">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long –** dokumento įmonės duomenų apsaugos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3621">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3622">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string –** dokumento plėtinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3622">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3623">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string –** dokumento plėtinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3623">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3624">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long –** iš anksto nustatytų failo formato reikšmių rinkinys (detalesnis nei plėtinio)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3624">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3625">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string –** vieta, kurioje saugomas dokumentas (SharePoint.com, live.net) galima tik „Office 365“ domenams</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3625">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3628">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string –** unikalus tapatybės identifikatorius, naudojamas veiksmui su bendrinamais dokumentais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3628">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3629">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long –** šablonas įvairiems pateikto dokumento IO, susietiems su žymėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3629">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long -** Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3630">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long –** iš anksto nustatytų reikšmių, nurodančių kokio tipo informacijos teisių valdymas taikomas šiam dokumentui, rinkinys (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3630">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3631">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool –** „true“, jeigu HTTP antraštė „IsCloudCollabEnabled“jau buvo gauta iš PARINKČIŲ užklausos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3631">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool -** True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3632">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool –** ar dokumentas buvo atidarytas palaipsniui (nauja funkcija, kuri atidaro dokumentą be būtinybės atsisiųsti visą dokumentą)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3632">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool -** Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3633">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool –** ar dokumentas palaiko redagavimą vienu metu, naudojant naują OCS paslaugą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3633">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool -** Is Document supports coauthoring using new OCS service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3635">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool –** ar dokumentas atidarytas iš aplanko, naudojančio „OneDrive“ taikomosios programos sinchronizavimo atsarginei kopijai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3635">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool -** Is document opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3637">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long –** iš anksto apibrėžtų išsamesnės vietos informacijos reikšmių rinkinys (Temp folder, Downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3637">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long -** Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3638">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long –** bendraautorių skaičius dokumento atidarymo metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3638">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long -** Number of coauthors at the time of opening of a document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3639">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long –** iš anksto apibrėžtų dokumento užšifravimo slaptažodžiu reikšmių rinkinys (None, Password to read, Password to edit) –</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3639">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long -** Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)-</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3642">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – nurodo, kaip buvo nustatytas realaus laiko kanalas (RTC) dabartiniam failui (išjungtas, nepalaikomas, pagal pageidavimą, visada įjungta, ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3642">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3650">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long –** dokumento dydis baitais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3650">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long -** Document size in bytes</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3652">**Data\_Doc\_StorageProviderId:string –** eilutė, nurodanti dokumento saugyklos teikėją, pvz., „DropBox“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3652">**Data\_Doc\_StorageProviderId:string -** A string that identifies the document's storage provider, like "DropBox"</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3669">Surinkti kiekvieną kartą, kai „PowerPoint“ įrašo naudodama modernų kodo kelią.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3669">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a save using the modern code path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3670">Apima sėkmingai arba nesėkmingai atlikto našumo metrikų ir susijusio dokumento metaduomenų įrašymo rezultato tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3670">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3671"> Nepavykus įrašymui, duomenys gali būti prarasti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3671"> Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3672">„Microsoft“ naudoja šiuos duomenis, kad užtikrintų, jog funkcija veikia kaip priklauso ir vartotojo turinys yra sėkmingai išlaikomas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3672">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3673">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3673">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3676">**Data\_BeforeSaveEvent:long –** laikas, skirtas pakelti dokumentą prieš įrašymo įvykį</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3676">**Data\_BeforeSaveEvent:long -** Time taken to raise Document Before Save Event</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3737">**Data\_MethodId:long –** nurodo vidinę informaciją kodo eilutės, kuri turėjo būti vykdoma paskutinė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3737">**Data\_MethodId:long -** Internally which line of code was last one to be executed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3740">**Data\_PerformPostSaveTimeMS:long –** laikas, skirtas funkcijoms po įrašymo atlikti (pranešimai, įrašų anuliavimas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3740">**Data\_PerformPostSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to perform post save functions (notifications, undo entries)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3743">**Data\_ReflectDocumentChangeTimeMS:long –** laikas, skirtas, kad įrašyti į UI pakeitimai būtų matomi (miniatiūrų publikavimas iš naujo ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3743">**Data\_ReflectDocumentChangeTimeMS:long -** Time taken to reflect saved changes to UI (repopulate thumbnails etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3744">**Data\_ReportStartTimeMS:long –** laikas, skirtas baigti įrašymo telemetrijos inicijavimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3744">**Data\_ReportStartTimeMS:long -** Time taken to finish initializing telemetry for save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3745">**Data\_ReportSuccessTimeMS:long –** laikas, skirtas sėkmingai įrašymo ataskaitai baigti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3745">**Data\_ReportSuccessTimeMS:long -** Time taken to finish reporting successful save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3746">**Data\_ResetDirtyFlagOnErrorTimeMS:long –** laikas, skirtas dokumento klaidos neatnaujintai žymei nustatyti iš naujo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3746">**Data\_ResetDirtyFlagOnErrorTimeMS:long -** Time taken to reset document dirty flag on error</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3750">**Data\_SavingWithFont:bool –** ar įrašome dokumentą su naujais įdėtaisiais šriftais?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3750">**Data\_SavingWithFont:bool-** Are we saving document with new embedded fonts?</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsaveas"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3754">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveAs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3754">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveAs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3755">Surinkti kiekvieną kartą, kai „PowerPoint“ atlieka operaciją įrašyti kaip.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3755">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a Save As.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3756">Apima sėkmingai arba nesėkmingai atlikto našumo metrikų ir susijusio dokumento metaduomenų įrašymo rezultato tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3756">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3757">Nepavykus įrašymui, duomenys gali būti prarasti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3757">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3758">„Microsoft“ naudoja šiuos duomenis, kad užtikrintų, jog funkcija veikia kaip priklauso ir vartotojo turinys yra sėkmingai išlaikomas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3758">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3759">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3759">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3760">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** – ar šis žurnalo įrašas turi visą reikiamą dokumento telemetriją (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3760">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** - Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3761">Jei ne, kodėl?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3761">If not, why?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3762">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** – veiklos veikimo metu neaptiktos vietinės išimtys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3762">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** - Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3763">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** – veiklos atskyrimo / neveikimo trukmė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3763">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** - Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3764">**Data_DstDoc_AccessMode:long** – nurodo, kaip šis dokumentas buvo atidarytas (tik skaityti | skaityti ir rašyti)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3764">**Data_DstDoc_AccessMode:long** - How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3765">**Data_DstDoc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** – iš anksto apibrėžtas reikšmių, nurodančių dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežastis, rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3765">**Data_DstDoc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3766">**Data_DstDoc_AsyncOpenKind:long** – nurodo, ar naujo debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3766">**Data_DstDoc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the new cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3767">**Data_DstDoc_ChunkingType:long** – nurodo, kaip dokumentas saugomas programoje „SharePoint“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3767">**Data_DstDoc_ChunkingType:long** - How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3768">**Data_DstDoc_EdpState:long** – dokumento įmonės duomenų apsaugos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3768">**Data_DstDoc_EdpState:long** - Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3769">**Data_DstDoc_Ext:string** – dokumento plėtinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3769">**Data_DstDoc_Ext:string** - Document extension</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3770">**Data_DstDoc_Extension:string** – dokumento plėtinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3770">**Data_DstDoc_Extension:string** - Document extension</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3771">**Data_DstDoc_FileFormat:long** – iš anksto nustatytų failo formato reikšmių rinkinys (detalesnis nei plėtinio)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3771">**Data_DstDoc_FileFormat:long** - Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3772">**Data_DstDoc_Fqdn:string** – vieta, kurioje saugomas dokumentas (SharePoint.com, live.net), galima tik „Office 365“ domenams</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3772">**Data_DstDoc_Fqdn:string** - Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3773">**Data_DstDoc_FqdnHash:string** – dokumento saugojimo vietos maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3773">**Data_DstDoc_FqdnHash:string** - Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3774">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityTelemetryId:string** – unikalusis vartotojo GUID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3774">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityTelemetryId:string** - Unique GUID of user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3775">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityUniqueId:string** – unikalusis tapatybės identifikatorius, naudojamas veiksmui su bendrinamais dokumentais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3775">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityUniqueId:string** - Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3776">**Data_DstDoc_IOFlags:long** – šablonas įvairiems pateikto dokumento IO, susietiems su žymėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3776">**Data_DstDoc_IOFlags:long** - Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3777">**Data_DstDoc_IrmRights:long** – iš anksto nustatytų reikšmių, nurodančių, kokio tipo informacijos teisių valdymas taikomas šiam dokumentui, rinkinys (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3777">**Data_DstDoc_IrmRights:long** - Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3778">**Data_DstDoc_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** – „teisinga“, jeigu HTTP antraštė „IsCloudCollabEnabled“jau buvo gauta iš PARINKČIŲ užklausos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3778">**Data_DstDoc_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** - True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3779">**Data_DstDoc_IsIncrementalOpen:bool** – nurodo, ar dokumentas buvo atidarytas palaipsniui (nauja funkcija, kuri atidaro dokumentą be būtinybės atsisiųsti visą dokumentą)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3779">**Data_DstDoc_IsIncrementalOpen:bool** - Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3780">**Data_DstDoc_IsOcsSupported:bool** – nurodo, ar dokumentas palaiko redagavimą vienu metu, naudojant naują OCS paslaugą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3780">**Data_DstDoc_IsOcsSupported:bool** - Is Document supports coauthoring using new OCS service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3781">**Data_DstDoc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool** – tikrina, ar dokumentas atidarytas iš vietinės talpyklos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3781">**Data_DstDoc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool** - verifies if document is being opened from local cache</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3782">**Data_DstDoc_IsSyncBacked:bool** – nurodo, ar dokumentas atidarytas iš aplanko, naudojančio „OneDrive“ taikomosios programos sinchronizavimo atsarginei kopijai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3782">**Data_DstDoc_IsSyncBacked:bool** - Is document opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3783">**Data_DstDoc_Location:long** – iš anksto apibrėžtas dokumento saugojimo vietos reikšmių rinkinys (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3783">**Data_DstDoc_Location:long** - Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3784">**Data_DstDoc_LocationDetails:long** – iš anksto apibrėžtas išsamesnės vietos informacijos reikšmių rinkinys (Temp folder, Downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3784">**Data_DstDoc_LocationDetails:long** - Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3785">**Data_DstDoc_NumberCoAuthors:long** – bendraautorių skaičius dokumento atidarymo metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3785">**Data_DstDoc_NumberCoAuthors:long** - Number of coauthors at the time of opening of a document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3786">**Data_DstDoc_PasswordFlags:long** – iš anksto apibrėžtas dokumento užšifravimo slaptažodžiu reikšmių rinkinys (None, Password to read, Password to edit)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3786">**Data_DstDoc_PasswordFlags:long** - Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3787">**Data_DstDoc_ReadOnlyReasons:long** – iš anksto apibrėžtas dokumento žymėjimo tik skaityti reikšmių rinkinys (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3787">**Data_DstDoc_ReadOnlyReasons:long** - Predefined set of values of why this document was marked read only (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3788">**Data_DstDoc_ResourceIdHash:string** – debesyje saugomų dokumentų išteklių identifikatoriaus maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3788">**Data_DstDoc_ResourceIdHash:string** - Hash of resource identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3789">**Data_DstDoc_ServerDocId:string** – debesyje saugomų dokumentų išteklių identifikatoriaus maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3789">**Data_DstDoc_ServerDocId:string** - immutable identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3790">**Data_DstDoc_ServerProtocol:long** – iš anksto apibrėžtas reikšmių, nurodančių, kuris protokolas naudojamas kreiptis į serverį, rinkinys (Http, „Cobalt“, WOPI ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3790">**Data_DstDoc_ServerProtocol:long** - Predefined set of values of which protocol is used to talk to server (Http, Cobalt, WOPI etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3791">**Data_DstDoc_ServerType:long** – iš anksto apibrėžtas serverio tipo reikšmių rinkinys („SharePoint“, „DropBox“ ar WOPI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3791">**Data_DstDoc_ServerType:long** - Predefined set of values of type of server (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3792">**Data_DstDoc_ServerVersion:long** – tikrina, ar serveryje naudojama „Office14“, „Office15“ arba „Office 16“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3792">**Data_DstDoc_ServerVersion:long** - verifies if server is based off Office14, Office15 or Office 16</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3793">**Data_DstDoc_SessionId:long** – generuotas GUID, identifikuojantis dokumento egzempliorių to paties proceso seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3793">**Data_DstDoc_SessionId:long** - generated GUID that Identifies the instance of the document within the same process session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3794">**Data_DstDoc_SharePointServiceContext:string** – nepermatoma eilutė, paprastai GridManagerID.FarmID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3794">**Data_DstDoc_SharePointServiceContext:string** - An opaque string, typically GridManagerID.FarmID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3795">Tinkama kliento ir serverio įvykių žurnalų koreliacijai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3795">Useful for correlating client side and server-side logs</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3796">**Data_DstDoc_SizeInBytes:long** – dokumento dydis baitais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3796">**Data_DstDoc_SizeInBytes:long** - Document size in bytes</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3797">**Data_DstDoc_SpecialChars:long** – šablonas, nurodantis specialiuosius dokumento URL arba kelio simbolius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3797">**Data_DstDoc_SpecialChars:long** - Bitmask indicating special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3798">**Data_DstDoc_StorageProviderId:string** – eilutė, nurodanti dokumento saugyklos teikėją, pvz., „DropBox“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3798">**Data_DstDoc_StorageProviderId:string** - A string that identifies the document's storage provider, like "DropBox"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3799">**Data_DstDoc_StreamAvailability:long** – iš anksto apibrėžtas dokumentų srauto būsenos reikšmių rinkinys (available, permanently disabled, not available)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3799">**Data_DstDoc_StreamAvailability:long** - Predefined set of values of status of document Stream(available, permanently disabled, not available)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3800">**Data_DstDoc_UrlHash:string** – debesyje saugomų dokumentų visų URL maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3800">**Data_DstDoc_UrlHash:string** - hash of full URL of documents stored in cloud</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsavelegacy"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3854">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveLegacy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3854">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveLegacy</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3855">Surinkti kiekvieną kartą, kai „PowerPoint“ įrašo naudodama senesnį kodo kelią.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3855">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a save using the legacy code path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3856">Apima sėkmingai arba nesėkmingai atlikto našumo metrikų ir susijusio dokumento metaduomenų įrašymo rezultato tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3856">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3857">Nepavykus įrašymui, duomenys gali būti prarasti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3857">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3858">„Microsoft“ naudoja šiuos duomenis, kad užtikrintų, jog funkcija veikia kaip priklauso ir vartotojo turinys yra sėkmingai išlaikomas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3858">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3859">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3859">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3860">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** – ar šis žurnalo įrašas turi visą reikiamą dokumento telemetriją (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3860">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** - Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3861">Jei ne, kodėl?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3861">If not, why?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3862">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** – veiklos veikimo metu neaptiktos vietinės išimtys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3862">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** - Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3863">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** – veiklos atskyrimo / neveikimo trukmė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3863">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** - Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3864">**Data_Doc_AccessMode:long** – nurodo, kaip šis dokumentas buvo atidarytas (tik skaityti | skaityti ir rašyti)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3864">**Data_Doc_AccessMode:long** - How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3865">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** – iš anksto apibrėžtas reikšmių, nurodančių dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežastis, rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3865">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3866">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3866">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3867">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType:long** – nurodo, kaip dokumentas saugomas programoje „SharePoint“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3867">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType:long** - How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3993">Renkama, kai PDF eksportavimo operacija baigta, ir joje yra informacijos apie operacijos sėkmę.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3993">Collected whenever an export PDF operation has completed and contains information about the success of the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3994">Ši informacija yra labai svarbi norint nustatyti, ar PDF eksportavimo operacijos sėkmingai vykdomos mūsų programoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3994">This information is critical to identify the success of export PDF operations for our application.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-3995">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-3995">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4067">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4067">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4068">**Data\_Surface** – darbinės srities, kuriai skirtas šios tarnybos pristatytas pranešimas, pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4068">**Data\_Surface** – Name of the surface that this service delivered message is meant for</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4069">**Data\_Flight** – ECS/CT testuojamo varianto identifikatorius, naudojamas pranešimui siųsti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4069">**Data\_Flight** – ECS/CT Flight identifier that was used to deliver this message</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4070">**Data\_CampaignId** – kampanijos, kurios dalis yra šis pranešimas, identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4070">**Data\_CampaignId** – identifier of the campaign that this message is part of</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4072">**Data\_TransactionId** – šios operacijos su tarnyba identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4072">**Data\_TransactionId** – identifier of this transaction with the service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4073">**Data\_TriggerPoint** – veiksmas, kuriame šis įvykis buvo užfiksuotas (gauto pranešimo palyginimas su rodomu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4073">**Data\_TriggerPoint** – The step in which this event was logged (message received vs message displayed)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4210">**Data\_Enable:bool**- „True“ nurodo, ar funkcija įjungta esamam vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4210">**Data\_Enable:bool**- true indicate the feature is enabled for current user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4212">**Data\_Flighted:bool** - „True“ nurodo, ar funkcija yra įjungta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4212">**Data\_Flighted:bool** - true indicates the feature is enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4214">**Data\_Subscriber:bool** - „True“ nurodo, ar vartotojas turi prenumeratos licenciją</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4214">**Data\_Subscriber:bool** - true indicates the user has subscription license</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4219">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool**– „True“ nurodo, jei atnaujinta diagrama iš pradžių buvo sukurta naudojant jungtį, pagrįstą sekos parinktimi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4219">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** - true if the refreshed diagram was originally created using connector based on sequence" option</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4222">**Data\_OverwriteSelected**:**bool** - „True“ nurodo, ar vartotojas atnaujinant diagramą pasirinko diagramos perrašymo parinktį</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4222">**Data\_OverwriteSelected**:**bool** - true if user selected overwrite diagram option during refresh</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4223">**Data\_WarningShown**:**bool** - „True“ nurodo, ar nebuvo jokių įspėjimų vartotojui atliekant duomenų atnaujinimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4223">**Data\_WarningShown**:**bool** - true if there was any warning shown to user during data refresh</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiosharedwritebacktoexcel"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4224">Office.Visio.Shared.WritebackToExcel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4224">Office.Visio.Shared.WritebackToExcel</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4225">Fiksuoja „Excel“ rašymo triktis, kai failas sukurtas naudojant DV.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4225">Captures Excel write back failures when file is created through DV.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-4226">Tai padeda mums derinti gedimus ir problemas įrašant duomenis į „Excel“ DV diagramoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-4226">This helps us debug the failures and issues in writing back data to Excel in a DV diagram.</span></span>
