#### <a name="officeextensibilitysandboxodpactivationhanging"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5066">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHanging</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5066">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHanging</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5067">Renka, kai paleisti „Office“ papildinį užtrunka netikėtai ilgai (> 5 sek.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5067">Collects when an Office add-in takes unexpectedly long to launch (>5 sec).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5068">Naudojama „Office“ papildinių paleidimo triktims aptikti ir pašalinti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5068">Used to detect and fix problems with Office add-ins launching.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5069">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5069">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5070">**AppId** – taikomosios programos ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5070">**AppId** - ID of the App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5071">**AppInfo** – duomenys, susiję su papildinio tipu (užduočių sritis arba be sąsajos, arba turinys ir t. t.) ir teikėjo tipu (domenas, „SharePoint“, failų sistema ir t. t.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5071">**AppInfo** - data regarding the type of add-in (task pane or UILess or in content etc.) and the provider type (omen, SharePoint, filesystem etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5072">**AppInstanceId** – taikomosios programos egzemplioriaus ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5072">**AppInstanceId** - ID of the app instance</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5073">**AssetId** – taikomosios programos ištekliaus ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5073">**AssetId** - asset ID of the app</span></span>

#### <a name="officeofficemobilefirstrunsetup"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5083">Office.OfficeMobile.FirstRunSetup</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5083">Office.OfficeMobile.FirstRunSetup</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5084">Pirmą kartą paleidus programą po įdiegimo, bus suaktyvintas šis reguliarių pranešimų įvykis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5084">The first run of the app after installation will trigger this heartbeat event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5085">Tai padės nustatyti diegimus ir automatinius miš senesnių programos versijų ir leis nustatyti klaidas automatiniame naujinime, įskaitant bibliotekos įkėlimus ir išplėtimo/kalbos paketo atsisiuntimo triktis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5085">It will help identify installs and auto upgrades from older versions of the app and enable us to identify errors in auto-upgrades, including library loads and expansion/language package download failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5086">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5086">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5087">**IsFlightAssigned** – Boolean reikšmė nustatanti, ar vartotojas buvo iš bet kurios iš dalies paskirtos skrydžio grupės, kuri gali suaktyvinti tam tikras funkcijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5087">**IsFlightAssigned** - Boolean value determining if the user was part of any preassigned flight group which can trigger exposure to certain experiences.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5088">**IsFRELoadSuccessful** – sveikasis skaičius, nurodantis rezultatų būseną</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5088">**IsFRELoadSuccessful** - integer mentioning the result state</span></span>

#### <a name="onenoteappappbootcomplete-previous-name-officeonenoteandroidappappbootcomplete-officeandroidearlytelemetryappbootcomplete"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5089">OneNote.App.AppBootComplete *(ankstesnis pavadinimas)*, Office.OneNote.Android.App.AppBootComplete, Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.AppBootComplete</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5089">OneNote.App.AppBootComplete *(previous name)*, Office.OneNote.Android.App.AppBootComplete, Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.AppBootComplete</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5090">Kritinis signalas, naudojamas siekiant užtikrinti, kad nauji vartotojai („Microsoft“ paskyra) gali sėkmingai paleisti ir naudoti „OneNote“ pirmą kartą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5090">The critical signal used to ensure new consumer users (Microsoft Account) can successfully launch and use OneNote for the first time.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5091">Tai naudojama siekiant užtikrinti regresijos aptikimą, kuris ypač svarbus programai „OneNote“ ir tarnybos sveikatai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5091">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5092">Jei vartotojai negali paleisti programos pirmą kartą, suaktyvinamas didelės svarbos incidentas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5092">If users can't launch the app for the first time, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5096">**ANY_DIALOG_SHOWN** – nurodo, ar paleidimo metu rodomas koks nors dialogo langas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5096">**ANY_DIALOG_SHOWN** - Indicates if any dialog is shown during boot time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5097">**APP_SUSPEND_DURING_EVENT** – nurodo, ar paleidimas buvo iš anksto ištuštintas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5097">**APP_SUSPEND_DURING_EVENT** - Indicates if the boot was pre-empted</span></span>

#### <a name="officesessionidproviderofficeprocesssessionstart"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5420">Office.SessionIdProvider.OfficeProcessSessionStart</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5420">Office.SessionIdProvider.OfficeProcessSessionStart</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5421">Taikoma visoms „Office“ „Windows“ pagrįstomis programomis: win32 ir UWP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5421">Applicable to all the Office windows-based applications: win32 and UWP</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5422">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5422">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5423">**OfficeProcessSessionStart** Siunčia pagrindinę informaciją į naują „Office“ seanso pradžią.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5423">**OfficeProcessSessionStart** sends basic information upon the start of a new Office session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5424">Naudojamas norint suskaičiuoti unikalius seansus, matomus šiais įrenginiais.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5424">This is used to count the number of unique sessions seen on a given device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5425">Jis naudojamas kaip pasikartojantis įvykis, kad užtikrintų, jog taikomoji programa paleista įrenginyje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5425">This is used as a heartbeat event to ensure that the application is running on a device or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5426">Be to, tai yra svarbus visos programos patikimumo signalas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5426">In addition, it serves as a critical signal for overall application reliability</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5427">**ProgramosSeansoVedikl** – konkrečios taikomosios programos seanso pradžios identifikatorius, naudojamas nuo proceso kūrimo pradžios ir iki proceso pabaigos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5427">**AppSessionGuid** - An identifier of a particular application session starting at process creation time and persisting until process end.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5428">Jis yra suformuotas kaip standartinis 128 bitų GUID, tik sudarytas iš 4 dalių.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5428">It is formatted as a standard 128-bit GUID but constructed of 4 parts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5429">Šios keturios dalys eil4s tvarka yra (1) 32 bitų proceso ID (2) 16 bitų seanso ID (3) 16 bitų įkrovos ID (4) 64 bitų proceso sukūrimo laikasm išreikštas UTC 100ns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5429">Those four parts in order are (1) 32 bit Process ID (2) 16 bit Session ID (3) 16 bit Boot ID (4) 64 bit Process creation time in UTC 100ns</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5430">**processSessionId** - Atsitiktinai sugeneruotas žinynas, skirtas programos seansui identifikuoti </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5430">**processSessionId** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5431">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** - Pastovi Bulio logikos vertė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5431">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** - Constant boolean value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5432">Visuomet „True“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5432">Always true.</span></span>

#### <a name="officesystemsessionhandoff"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5433">Office.System.SessionHandoff</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5433">Office.System.SessionHandoff</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5434">Nurodo, kad dabartinis „Office“ seansas yra perdavimo seansas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5434">Indicates that the current Office session is a handoff session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5435">Tai reiškia, kad vartotojo prašymo atidaryti dokumentą tvarkymas perduodamas į tos pačios programos jau veikiantį egzempliorių.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5435">This means that handling of a user's request to open a document is being handed off to an already running instance of the same application.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5436">Renkami toliau apibūdintų laukų duomenys.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5436">The following fields are collected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5437">**ParentSessionId** – seanso, kuris perims vartotojų užklausos tvarkymą, ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5437">**ParentSessionId** - The ID of the session that will be taking over handling of the users' request.</span></span>

#### <a name="officetelemetryengineisprelaunch"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5438">Office.TelemetryEngine.IsPreLaunch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5438">Office.TelemetryEngine.IsPreLaunch</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5439">Tinka Office UWP taikomosioms programoms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5439">Applicable for Office UWP applications.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5440">Šis įvykis sužadinamas, kai „Office“ programa paleidžiama pirmą kartą po atnaujinimo ar įdiegimo iš parduotuvės.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5440">This event is fired when an Office application is initiated for the first-time post upgrade/install from the store.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5441">Tai yra pagrindinės diagnostikos duomenų dalis, naudojama seansui stebėti, ar jis pradėtas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5441">This is part of basic diagnostic data, used to track whether a session is launch session or not.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5442">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5442">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5443">**appVersionBuild** – taikomosios programos komponavimo versijos numeris.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5443">**appVersionBuild** - The app build version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5444">**appVersionMajor** – taikomosios programos pagrindinės versijos numeris.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5444">**appVersionMajor** - The app major version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5445">**appVersionMajor** – taikomosios programos papildomos versijos numeris.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5445">**appVersionMinor** - The app minor version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5446">**appVersionRev** – taikomosios programos peržiūros versijos numeris.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5446">**appVersionRev** - The app revision version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5447">**sessionID** – atsitiktinai sugeneruotas GUID, skirtas nustatyti taikomosios programos seansą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5447">**SessionID** - Randomly generated GUID to identify the app session</span></span>

#### <a name="officetelemetryenginesessionhandoff"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5448">Office.TelemetryEngine.SessionHandOff</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5448">Office.TelemetryEngine.SessionHandOff</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5449">Taikoma „Win32“ „Office“ taikomosioms programoms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5449">Applicable to Win32 Office applications.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5450">Šis įvykis padeda suprasti, ar buvo sukurtas naujas seansas, kuris tvarkys vartotojų inicijuotą failo atidarymo įvykį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5450">This event helps us understand whether there was a new session created to handle a user-initiated file open event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5451">Tai svarbi diagnostinė informacija, naudojama patikimumo signalui gauti ir užtikrinti, kad programa veiktų taip, kaip tikėtasi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5451">It is a critical diagnostic information that is used to derive reliability signal and ensure that the application is working as expected.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5452">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5452">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5453">**appVersionBuild** – taikomosios programos komponavimo versijos numeris.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5453">**appVersionBuild** - The app build version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5454">**appVersionMajor** – taikomosios programos pagrindinės versijos numeris.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5454">**appVersionMajor** - The app major version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5455">**appVersionMajor** – taikomosios programos papildomos versijos numeris.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5455">**appVersionMinor** - The app minor version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5456">**appVersionRev** – taikomosios programos peržiūros versijos numeris.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5456">**appVersionRev** - The app revision version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5457">**sessionID** – atsitiktinai sugeneruotas GUID, skirtas nustatyti taikomosios programos seansą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5457">**childSessionID** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5458">**parentSessionId** – atsitiktinai sugeneruotas GUID, skirtas nustatyti taikomosios programos seansą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5458">**parentSessionId** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiovisioiosappboottime"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5459">Office.Visio.VisioIosAppBootTime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5459">Office.Visio.VisioIosAppBootTime</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5460">Jis suaktyvinamas kiekvieną kartą, kai paleidžiama „Visio iOS“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5460">This is triggered every time the Visio iOS application boots.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5461">Labai svarbu suprasti taikomosios programos „Visio iOS“ paleidimo rezultatus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5461">It is essential to understand boot performance of the Visio iOS app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5462">Naudojama prasto veikimo trikčių diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5462">Used to troubleshoot poor performance.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5463">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5463">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5464">**Data_AppBootTime** – taikomosios programos paleidimo trukmė, išreikšta milisekundėmis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5464">**Data_AppBootTime** - Duration taken for app to boot, in milliseconds.</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiovisioiosappresumetime"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5465">Office.Visio.VisioIosAppResumeTime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5465">Office.Visio.VisioIosAppResumeTime</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5466">Šis įvykis paleidžiamas kiekvieną kartą, kai taikomoji programa „Visio iOS“ tęsia fokusavimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5466">This event is triggered every time the Visio iOS app resumes focus.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5467">Būtina išmatuoti taikomosios programos tęsimo našumą ir taikomosios programos „Visio iOS“ trikčių diagnostikos našumo problemas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5467">It is essential to measure app resume performance and troubleshoot performance issues of Visio iOS app.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5468">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5468">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5469">**Data_AppResumeTime** – programos trukmė iki tęsimo, išreikšta milisekundėmis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5469">**Data_AppResumeTime** - Duration for app to resume in milliseconds.</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopencmdfilemrupriv"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5470">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenCmdFileMruPriv</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5470">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenCmdFileMruPriv</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5471">Šis įvykis nurodo „Office Word“ atidaryti dokumentą iš vėliausiai naudoto (MRU) sąrašo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5471">This event indicates Office Word opens a document from the Most Recent Used (MRU) list.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5472">Jame taip pat yra svarbių failo atidarymo našumo duomenų ir yra programėlės pradžios įvykis vertinant iš vartotojo perspektyvos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5472">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5473">Įvykis stebi, ar file-open-from-MRU veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5473">The event monitors whether fileopen-from-MRU is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5474">Jis taip pat naudojamas mėnesio aktyviems vartotojams / įrenginiams ir debesies patikimumo rodikliams apskaičiuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5474">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5475">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5475">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5476">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – nurodo, ar įvykyje galima tinkamai užpildyti kitų dokumentų telemetrijos susijusias reikšmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5476">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5477">Naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5477">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5478">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – baitų (suglaudintų), kurie, kaip manoma, gali atidaryti failą, skaičius, nepaisant, ar mes juos gausime iki tol, kol vartotojas nori pradėti redaguoti arba galbūt įrašyti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5478">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5479">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – baitų (suglaudintų), kuriuos naudodami galėtume atidaryti failą, skaičius, tačiau norint, kad tai įvyktų, reikės daug investuoti į kodą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5479">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5480">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – baitų (suglaudintų) skaičius, kuriuos privalome turėti prieš pradėdami atidaryti failą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5480">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5481">**Data_BytesUnknown** – baitų skaičius dokumento dalyse, kurių nesitikėjome rasti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5481">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5482">**Data_DetachedDuration** – nurodo, kiek laiko gijoje nebuvo veiklos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5482">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5483">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – nurodo, ar dokumentas yra skirtas tik skaityti, ar redaguojamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5483">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read-only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5484">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – iš anksto nustatytų dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežasčių reikšmių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5484">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5485">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5485">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5486">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – elementai, naudojami nuosekliam dokumento atidarymui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5486">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5487">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – dokumentui taikomas elektroninių duomenų apsaugos parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5487">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5488">**Data_Doc_Ext** – dokumento plėtinys (docx, xlsb, pptx ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5488">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5489">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – failo formato protokolo versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5489">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5490">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – „OneDrive“ arba „SharePoint“ interneto domeno vardas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5490">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5491">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – kliento identifikuojamo domeno vardo vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5491">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5492">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – vartotojo tapatybės, naudojamos atidarymui, vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5492">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5493">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – įrašo, kaip dokumentas buvo atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5493">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5494">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – informuoja apie į talpyklą įtrauktas žymes, naudotas nustatyti užklausos parinktis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5494">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5495">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – veiksmai, leidžiami elektroninių duomenų apsaugos strategijos, kuri buvo taikyta dokumentui arba vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5495">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5496">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – žymė, nurodanti, kad dokumentas buvo palaipsniui atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5496">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5497">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – žymė nurodanti, kad dokumentą palaiko bendradarbiavimo tarnyba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5497">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5498">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – žymė, nurodanti, kad atidaryta autonominė dokumento kopija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5498">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5499">**Data.Doc.IsSyncBacked –** žymė, nurodanti, kad automatiškai sinchronizuota dokumento kopija yra kompiuteryje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5499">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Flag indicating that an auto-synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5500">**Data_Doc_Location** – nurodo tarnybą, pateikusią dokumentą („OneDrive“, „File Server“, „SharePoint“ ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5500">**Data_Doc_Location** - Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5501">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** – nurodo įrenginyje saugomo dokumento žinomą aplanką</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5501">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** - Indicates which Known Folder provided a locally stored document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5502">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** – skaičiuoja bendro redagavimo seanso metu bendradarbiaujančių vartotojų skaičių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5502">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** - Count of the number of fellow users in a collaborative editing session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5503">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** – nurodo, ar nustatytas skaitymo arba skaitymo / rašymo slaptažodžio žymių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5503">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** - Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5504">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – dokumento atidarymo tik kaip skaitomo priežastys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5504">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5505">**Data.Doc.ResourceIdHash** – anonimiškai pateiktų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5505">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - An anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5506">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – nurodo, kaip buvo nustatytas realaus laiko kanalas (RTC) dabartiniam failui (išjungtas, nepalaikomas, pagal pageidavimą, visada įjungta, ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5506">**Data_Doc_RtcType** -  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5507">**Data.Doc.ServerDocId** – nekintamų anonimiškai pateiktų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5507">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - An immutable anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5508">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – protokolo versija, naudojama norint susisiekti su tarnyba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5508">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - the protocol version used to communicate with the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5509">**Data.Doc.ServerType** – tarnybą siūlančio serverio tipas („SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, WOPI ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5509">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - the type of the server offering the service (SharePoint, OneDrive, WOPI, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5510">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – serverio versija, siūlanti tarnybą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5510">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - the server version offering the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5511">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – nustato konkretų dokumentų redagavimo seansą visame seanse</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5511">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - Identifies a specific document edit session within the full session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5512">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – „SharePoint Online“ užklausų diagnostinė informacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5512">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - Diagnostic information from SharePoint Online requests</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5514">**Data.Doc.SpecialChars** – dokumento URL specialiųjų simbolių indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5514">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - Indicator of special chars in the document's URL</span></span>
