- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5520">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** – sveikasis skaičius, nurodantis priežastį, kodėl failas buvo priverstinai atidarytas skaitymo / rašymo režimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5520">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** - Integer value representing the reason why the file was forced into read/write mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5521">**Data_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure** – nurodo, kad atidaryti pavyko pašalinus triktį, įvykusią atidarant dokumentą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5521">**Data_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure** - Indicates that open succeeded after repairing a failure while opening the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5522">**Data_LastLoggedTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo žymės vieta, naudojama nustatyti, kada dukart nepavyksta bandymas atidaryti (naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5522">**Data_LastLoggedTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify when we try to fail the open twice (used for data quality diagnostics)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5523">**Data_LinkStyles** – nurodo, ar mes susieti su šablono stiliais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5523">**Data_LinkStyles** - Indicates whether we are linking to the template styles</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5524">**Data_MainPdod** – dokumento identifikatorius vykstant „Office Word“ procesui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5524">**Data_MainPdod** - The document identifier in Office Word process</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5525">**Data_Measurements** – užkoduota eilutė, kurioje pateiktas skirtingų dalių atidarymo laiko suskirstymas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5525">**Data_Measurements** - Encoded string containing the time breakdown of the different parts of open.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5526">Skirta našumui vertinti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5526">Used to measure performance.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5527">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** – klaida, kuri yra išjungia dokumento perkėlimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5527">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** - Error that is disabling move for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5528">**Data_MoveFlightEnabled** – nurodo, ar įjungta perkėlimo testavimo funkcija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5528">**Data_MoveFlightEnabled** - Whether the flight for the move feature is enabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5529">**Data_PartsUnknown** – dokumento dalių, iš kurių nepavyko gauti duomenų, skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5529">**Data_PartsUnknown** - the number of document parts that we couldn't get data for</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5530">**Data_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo vietos žymė, naudojama vietai kode, kurioje stengiamės sutvarkyti failą prieš jį atidarant, identifikuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5530">**Data_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify the place in code where we attempt to fix the file before opening it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5531">**Data_RenameDisabledReason** – klaida, dėl kurios šiam dokumentui išjungiamas pervardijimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5531">**Data_RenameDisabledReason** - Error that is causing for rename to be disabled for this document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5532">**Data_RenameFlightEnabled** – nurodo, ar įjungta pervardijimo testavimo funkcija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5532">**Data_RenameFlightEnabled** - Whether the flight for the rename feature is enabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5533">**Data_SecondaryTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo vietos žymė, naudojama papildomiems trikties duomenims atidaryti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5533">**Data_SecondaryTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to add additional failure data for open</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5534">**Data_TemplateFormat** – šablono failo, kuriuo pagrįstas dokumentas, formatas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5534">**Data_TemplateFormat** - File format of the template that the document is based on.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5535">**Data_UsesNormal** – nurodo, ar atidarytas dokumentas pagrįstas įprastu šablonu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5535">**Data_UsesNormal** - Indicates whether the open document is based on the normal template</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5536">**PathData_Doc_StreamAvailability** – indikatorius, nurodantis, ar dokumentų srautas yra pasiekiamas arba išjungtas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5536">**PathData_Doc_StreamAvailability** - Indicator if document stream is available/disabled</span></span>


#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenffileopenxstzcore"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5537">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenFFileOpenXstzCore</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5537">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenFFileOpenXstzCore</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5538">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad „Office Word“ atidaro dokumentą, kurį vartotojas dukart spustelėjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5538">This event indicates Office Word opens a document who is double clicked by a user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5539">Jame taip pat yra svarbių failo atidarymo našumo duomenų ir yra programėlės pradžios įvykis vertinant iš vartotojo perspektyvos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5539">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5540">Įvykis stebi, ar funkcija file-open-from-file-double-click veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5540">The event monitors whether file-openfrom-file-double-click is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5541">Jis taip pat naudojamas mėnesio aktyviems vartotojams / įrenginiams ir debesies patikimumo rodikliams apskaičiuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5541">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5542">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5542">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5543">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – nurodo, ar įvykyje galima tinkamai užpildyti kitų dokumentų telemetrijos susijusias reikšmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5543">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5544">Naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5544">Used for data quality diagnostics</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5545">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – baitų (suglaudintų), kurie, kaip manoma, gali atidaryti failą, skaičius, nepaisant, ar mes juos gausime iki tol, kol vartotojas nori pradėti redaguoti arba galbūt įrašyti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5545">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5546">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – baitų (suglaudintų), kuriuos naudodami galėtume atidaryti failą, skaičius, tačiau norint, kad tai įvyktų, reikės daug investuoti į kodą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5546">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5547">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – baitų (suglaudintų) skaičius, kuriuos privalome turėti prieš pradėdami atidaryti failą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5547">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5548">**Data_BytesUnknown** – baitų skaičius dokumento dalyse, kurių nesitikėjome rasti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5548">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5549">**Data_DetachedDuration** – nurodo, kiek laiko gijoje nebuvo veiklos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5549">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5550">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – nurodo, ar dokumentas yra skirtas tik skaityti, ar redaguojamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5550">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read-only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5551">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – iš anksto nustatytų dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežasčių reikšmių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5551">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5552">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5552">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5553">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – elementai, naudojami nuosekliam dokumento atidarymui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5553">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5554">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – dokumentui taikomas elektroninių duomenų apsaugos parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5554">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5555">**Data_Doc_Ext** – dokumento plėtinys (docx, xlsb, pptx ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5555">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5556">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – failo formato protokolo versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5556">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5557">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – „OneDrive“ arba „SharePoint“ interneto domeno vardas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5557">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5558">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – kliento identifikuojamo domeno vardo vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5558">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5559">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – informuoja apie į talpyklą įtrauktas žymes, naudotas nustatyti užklausos parinktis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5559">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5560">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – vartotojo tapatybės, naudojamos atidarymui, vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5560">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5561">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – įrašo, kaip dokumentas buvo atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5561">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5562">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – veiksmai, leidžiami elektroninių duomenų apsaugos strategijos, kuri buvo taikyta dokumentui arba vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5562">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5563">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – žymė, nurodanti, kad dokumentas buvo palaipsniui atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5563">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5564">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – žymė nurodanti, kad dokumentą palaiko bendradarbiavimo tarnyba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5564">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5565">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – žymė, nurodanti, kad atidaryta autonominė dokumento kopija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5565">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5566">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – žymė, nurodanti, kad automatiškai sinchronizuota dokumento kopija yra kompiuteryje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5566">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5567">**Data_Doc_Location** – nurodo tarnybą, pateikusią dokumentą („OneDrive“, „File Server“, „SharePoint“ ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5567">**Data_Doc_Location** - Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint etc.)</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5568">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** – nurodo įrenginyje saugomo dokumento žinomą aplanką</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5568">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** - Indicates which Known Folder provided a locally stored document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5569">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** – skaičiuoja bendro redagavimo seanso metu bendradarbiaujančių vartotojų skaičių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5569">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** - Count of the number of fellow users in a collaborative editing session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5570">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** – nurodo, ar nustatytas skaitymo arba skaitymo / rašymo slaptažodžio žymių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5570">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** - Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5571">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – dokumento atidarymo tik kaip skaitomo priežastys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5571">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5572">**Data.Doc.ResourceIdHash** – anonimiškai pateiktų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5572">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - An anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5573">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – nurodo, kaip buvo nustatytas realaus laiko kanalas (RTC) dabartiniam failui (išjungtas, nepalaikomas, pagal pageidavimą, visada įjungta, ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5573">**Data_Doc_RtcType** -  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5574">**Data.Doc.ServerDocId** – nekintamų anonimiškai pateiktų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5574">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - An immutable anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5575">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – protokolo versija, naudojama norint susisiekti su tarnyba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5575">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - the protocol version used to communicate with the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5576">**Data_Doc_ServerType** – tarnybą siūlančio serverio tipas („SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, WOPI ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5576">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - the type of the server offering the service (SharePoint, OneDrive, WOPI etc.)</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5577">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – serverio versija, siūlanti tarnybą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5577">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - the server version offering the service</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5578">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – nustato konkretų dokumentų redagavimo seansą visame seanse</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5578">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - Identifies a specific document edit session within the full session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5579">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – „SharePoint Online“ užklausų diagnostinė informacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5579">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - Diagnostic information from SharePoint Online requests</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5580">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – dokumento dydžio indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5580">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - Indicator of document size</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5581">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – dokumento URL arba kelio specialiųjų simbolių indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5581">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - Indicator of special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5582">**Data_Doc_StreamAvailability** – indikatorius, nurodantis, ar dokumentų srautas yra pasiekiamas arba išjungtas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5582">**Data_Doc_StreamAvailability** - Indicator if document stream is available/disabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5583">**Data_Doc_SyncBackedType** – dokumento tipo indikatorius (vietinis arba pagrįstas tarnyba)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5583">**Data_Doc_SyncBackedType** - Indicator as to the type of document (local or service based)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5584">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – vienpusė maiša, skirta „naïve“ dokumento identifikatoriui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5584">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - One-way hash to create a naïve document identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5585">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** – apima unikalų WOPI tarnybos teikėjo identifikatorių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5585">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - Contains unique identifier of WOPI service provider</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5586">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** – pirmojo redaktoriaus, dėl kurio buvo išjungtas pervardijimas, identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5586">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** - Identifier of the first editor that caused for rename to be disabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5587">**Data_EditorsCount** – dokumento redaktorių skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5587">**Data_EditorsCount** - Number of editors in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5588">**Data_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure** – nurodo, kad atidaryti pavyko pašalinus triktį, įvykusią atidarant dokumentą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5588">**Data_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure** - Indicates that open succeeded after repairing a failure while opening the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5589">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** – sveikasis skaičius, nurodantis priežastį, kodėl failas buvo priverstinai atidarytas skaitymo / rašymo režimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5589">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** - Integer value representing the reason why the file was forced into read/write mode</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5590">**Data_LastLoggedTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo žymės vieta, naudojama nustatyti, kada dukart nepavyksta bandymas atidaryti (naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5590">**Data_LastLoggedTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify when we try to fail the open twice (used for data quality diagnostics)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5591">**Data_LinkStyles** – nurodo, ar mes susieti su šablono stiliais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5591">**Data_LinkStyles** - Indicates whether we are linking to the template styles</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5592">**Data_MainPdod** – dokumento identifikatorius vykstant „Office Word“ procesui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5592">**Data_MainPdod** - The document identifier in Office Word process</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5593">**Data_Measurements** – užkoduota eilutė, kurioje pateiktas skirtingų dalių atidarymo laiko suskirstymas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5593">**Data_Measurements** - Encoded string containing the time breakdown of the different parts of open.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5594">Skirta našumui vertinti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5594">Used to measure performance.</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5595">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** – klaida, kuri yra išjungia dokumento perkėlimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5595">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** - Error that is disabling move for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5596">**Data_MoveFlightEnabled** – nurodo, ar įjungta perkėlimo testavimo funkcija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5596">**Data_MoveFlightEnabled** - Whether the flight for the move feature is enabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5597">**Data_PartsUnknown** – dokumento dalių, iš kurių nepavyko gauti duomenų, skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5597">**Data_PartsUnknown** - the number of document parts that we couldn't get data for</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5598">**Data_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo vietos žymė, naudojama vietai kode, kurioje stengiamės sutvarkyti failą prieš jį atidarant, identifikuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5598">**Data_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify the place in code where we attempt to fix the file before opening it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5599">**Data_RenameDisabledReason** – klaida, dėl kurios šiam dokumentui išjungiamas pervardijimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5599">**Data_RenameDisabledReason** - Error that is causing for rename to be disabled for this document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5600">**Data_RenameFlightEnabled** – nurodo, ar įjungta pervardijimo testavimo funkcija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5600">**Data_RenameFlightEnabled** - Whether the flight for the rename feature is enabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5601">**Data_SecondaryTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo vietos žymė, naudojama papildomiems trikties duomenims atidaryti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5601">**Data_SecondaryTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to add additional failure data for open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5602">**Data_TemplateFormat** – šablono failo, kuriuo pagrįstas dokumentas, formatas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5602">**Data_TemplateFormat** - File format of the template that the document is based on.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5603">**Data_UsesNormal** – nurodo, ar atidarytas dokumentas pagrįstas įprastu šablonu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5603">**Data_UsesNormal** - Indicates whether the open document is based on the normal template.</span></span>


#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenifrinitargs"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5604">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenIfrInitArgs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5604">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenIfrInitArgs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5605">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad „Office Word“ atidaro dokumentą naudojant COM aktyvinimą arba komandinę eilutę.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5605">This event indicates Office Word opens a document via COM activation or command line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5606">Jame taip pat yra svarbūs failo atidarymo našumo duomenys ir yra programėlės pradžios įvykis vertinant iš vartotojo perspektyvos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5606">It also contains critical file open performance data, and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5607">Įvykis stebi, ar file-open-from-command-line veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5607">The event monitors whether file-open-from-command-line is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5608">Jis taip pat naudojamas mėnesio aktyviems vartotojams / įrenginiams ir debesies patikimumo rodikliams apskaičiuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5608">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5609">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5609">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5610">**Data\_AddDocTelemRes –** nurodo, ar įvykyje galima tinkamai užpildyti kitų dokumentų telemetrijos susijusias reikšmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5610">**Data\_AddDocTelemRes -** Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5611">Naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5611">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5612">**Data\_BytesAsynchronous -** Baitų (suglaudintų), kurie, kaip manoma, gali atidaryti failą, skaičius, nepaisant, ar mes juos gausime, kol vartotojas nori pradėti redaguoti arba galbūt įrašyti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5612">**Data\_BytesAsynchronous -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5613">**Data\_BytesAsynchronousWithWork -** Baitų (suglaudintų), kuriuos naudodami galėtume atidaryti failą, skaičius, tačiau norint, kad tai įvyktų, reikės daug investuoti į kodą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5613">**Data\_BytesAsynchronousWithWork -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5614">**Data\_BytesSynchronous -** Baitų (suglaudintų) skaičius, kuriuos privalome turėti prieš pradėdami atidaryti failą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5614">**Data\_BytesSynchronous -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5615">**Data\_BytesUnknown –** baitų skaičius dokumentų dalyse, kurių nesitikėjome rasti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5615">**Data\_BytesUnknown -** Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5616">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode -** Dokumentas yra skirtas tik skaityti / redaguoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5616">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode -** Document is read only/editable</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5617">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons –** iš anksto nustatytų dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežasčių reikšmių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5617">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5618">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5618">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5619">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType –** vienetai, naudojami nuosekliam dokumento atidarymui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5619">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType -** Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5620">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState -** Dokumentui taikomas elektroninių duomenų apsaugos parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5620">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState -** Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5621">**Data\_Doc\_Ext -** Dokumento plėtinys (docx / xlsb / pptx ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5621">**Data\_Doc\_Ext -** Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5622">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat -** Failo formato protokolo versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5622">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat -** File format protocol version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5623">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn –** „OneDrive“ arba „SharePoint“ interneto domeno vardas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5623">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn -** OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5624">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash –** kliento identifikuojamo domeno vardo vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5624">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash -** One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5625">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags -** Informuoja apie į talpyklą įtrauktas žymes, naudotas užklausos parinktims nustatyti </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5625">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags -** Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5626">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId -** Vartotojo tapatybės, naudojamos atidarymui, vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5626">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId -** A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5627">**Data\_Doc\_InitializationScenario -** Įrašo, kaip dokumentas buvo atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5627">**Data\_Doc\_InitializationScenario -** Records how the document was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5628">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights –** veiksmai, leidžiami elektroninių duomenų apsaugos strategijos, kurie buvo taikyti dokumentui / vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5628">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights -** Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5629">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen -** Žymė, nurodanti, kad dokumentas buvo palaipsniui atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5629">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen -** Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5630">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported -** Žyma, nurodanti, kad dokumentas palaikomas bendradarbiavimo tarnybos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5630">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported -** Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5631">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy -** Žyma, nurodanti, kad autonominė dokumento kopija atidaryta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5631">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy -** Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5632">**Duomenų\_ad\_IsSyncBacked -** žyma, nurodanti, kad automatiškai sinchronizuota dokumento kopija yra kompiuteryje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5632">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked -** Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5633">**Data\_Doc\_Location -** Nurodo, kuri tarnyba teikia dokumentą („OneDrive“, failų serveris, „SharePoint“)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5633">**Data\_Doc\_Location -** Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5634">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails -** Nurodo, kuriuose žinomuose aplankuose yra vietoje saugomų dokumentų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5634">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails -** Indicates which Known Folder provided a locally stored document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5635">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors -** Skaičiuoja bendro redagavimo seanso metu bendradarbiaujančių vartotojų skaičių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5635">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors -** Count of the number of fellow users in a collaborative editing session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5636">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags –** nurodo, ar nustatytas skaitymo arba skaitymo / rašymo slaptažodžio žymų rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5636">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags -** Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5637">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons -** Priežastys, kodėl dokumentas buvo atidarytas tik kaip skaitomas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5637">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons -** Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5638">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash -** Anonimizuotų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5638">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash -** An anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5639">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – nurodo, kaip buvo nustatytas realaus laiko kanalas (RTC) dabartiniam failui (išjungtas, nepalaikomas, pagal pageidavimą, visada įjungta, ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5639">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5640">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId -** Nekintamų anonimizuotų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5640">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId -** An immutable anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5641">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol -** Protokolo versija, naudojama norint susisiekti su tarnyba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5641">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol -** the protocol version used to communicate with the service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5642">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType –** tarnybą siūlančio serverio tipas („SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, WOPI ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5642">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType -** the type of the server offering the service (SharePoint, OneDrive, WOPI etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5643">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion -** Serverio versija, siūlanti tarnybą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5643">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion -** the server version offering the service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5644">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId -** Serverio versija, siūlanti tarnybą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5644">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId -** the server version offering the service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5645">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext -** Diagnostinė informacija iš „SharePoint Online“ užklausų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5645">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext -** Diagnostic information from SharePoint Online requests</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5646">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes –** dokumento dydžio indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5646">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes -** Indicator of document size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5647">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars –** dokumento URL arba kelio specialiųjų simbolių indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5647">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars -** Indicator of special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5648">**Data\_Doc\_StreamAvailability –** indikatorius, nurodantis, ar dokumentų srautas yra pasiekiamas arba išjungtas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5648">**Data\_Doc\_StreamAvailability -** Indicator if document stream is available/disabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5649">**Data\_Doc\_SyncBackedType –** dokumento tipo indikatorius (vietinis arba pagrįstas tarnyba)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5649">**Data\_Doc\_SyncBackedType -** Indicator as to the type of document (local or service based)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5650">**Data\_Doc\_UrlHash –** vienpusė maiša, skirta „naïve“ dokumento identifikatoriui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5650">**Data\_Doc\_UrlHash -** One-way hash to create a naïve document identifier</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5651">**Data\_Doc\_WopiServiceId -** Apima unikalų WOPI tarnybos teikėjo identifikatorių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5651">**Data\_Doc\_WopiServiceId -** Contains unique identifier of WOPI service provider</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5652">**Data\_EditorDisablingRename -** Pirmojo redaktoriaus, dėl kurio buvo išjungtas pervardijimas, identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5652">**Data\_EditorDisablingRename -** Identifier of the first editor that caused for rename to be disabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5653">**Data\_EditorsCount -** Dokumento redaktorių skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5653">**Data\_EditorsCount -** Number of editors in the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5654">**Data\_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure -** Nurodo, kad atidaryti pavyko pašalinus triktį, įvykusią atidarant dokumentą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5654">**Data\_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure -** Indicates that open succeeded after repairing a failure while opening the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5655">**Data\_ForceReadWriteReason -** Sveikojo skaičiaus vertė, nurodanti priežastį, kodėl failas buvo priverstinai atidarytas skaitymo / rašymo režimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5655">**Data\_ForceReadWriteReason -** Integer value representing the reason why the file was forced into read/write mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5656">**Data\_LastLoggedTag -** Unikali kodo iškvietimo žymės vieta, naudojama nustatyti, kada dukart nepavyksta bandymas atidaryti (naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5656">**Data\_LastLoggedTag -** Unique tag for code call site used to identify when we try to fail the open twice (used for data quality diagnostics)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5657">**Data\_LinkStyles -** Nurodo, ar mes susieti su šablono stiliais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5657">**Data\_LinkStyles -** Indicates whether we are linking to the template styles</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5658">**Data\_MainPdod -** Dokumento identifikatorius vykstant „Office Word“ procesui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5658">**Data\_MainPdod -** The document identifier in Office Word process</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5659">**Data\_Measurements -** Užkoduota eilutė, kurioje yra skirtingų dalių atidarymo laiko suskirstymas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5659">**Data\_Measurements -** Encoded string containing the time breakdown of the different parts of open.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5660">Skirtas diagnozuoti atvirai veiklai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5660">Used to diagnose open performance.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5661">**Data\_MoveDisabledReason -** Klaida, kuri yra išjungia dokumento perkėlimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5661">**Data\_MoveDisabledReason -** Error that is disabling move for the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5662">**Data\_MoveFlightEnabled -** Ar įjungta perkėlimo testavimo funkcija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5662">**Data\_MoveFlightEnabled -** Whether the flight for the move feature is enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5663">**Data\_PartsUnknown –** dokumentų dalių, iš kurių nepavyko gauti duomenų, skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5663">**Data\_PartsUnknown -** the number of document parts that we couldn't get data for</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5664">**Data\_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag -** Unikali kodo iškvietimo vietos žymė, naudojama vietai kode, kurioje stengiamės sutvarkyti failą prieš jį atidarant, identifikuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5664">**Data\_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag -** Unique tag for code call site used to identify the place in code where we attempt to fix the file before opening it</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5665">**Data\_RenameDisabledReason -** Klaida, atsirandanti, kai pervardijimas šiam dokumentui išjungtas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5665">**Data\_RenameDisabledReason -** Error that is causing for rename to be disabled for this document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5666">**Data\_RenameFlightEnabled -** Ar įjungta pervardijimo testavimo funkcija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5666">**Data\_RenameFlightEnabled -** Whether the flight for the rename feature is enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5667">**Data\_SecondaryTag -** Unikali kodo iškvietimo vietos žymė, naudojama papildomiems trikties duomenims atidaryti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5667">**Data\_SecondaryTag -** Unique tag for code call site used to add additional failure data for open.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5668">**Data\_TemplateFormat -** Šablono failo formatas, kuriuo pagrįstas dokumentas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5668">**Data\_TemplateFormat -** File format of the template that the document is based on.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5669">**Data\_UsesNormal -** Nurodo, ar atidarytas dokumentas pagrįstas įprastu šablonu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5669">**Data\_UsesNormal -** Indicates whether the open document is based on the normal template.</span></span>


#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenloadfile"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5670">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenLoadFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5670">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenLoadFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5671">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad „Office Word“ atidaro dokumentą naudojant dialogo langą Atidaryti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5671">This event indicates Office Word opens a document via Open dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5672">Jame taip pat yra svarbių failo atidarymo našumo duomenų ir yra programėlės pradžios įvykis vertinant iš vartotojo perspektyvos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5672">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5673">Įvykis stebi, ar file-open-from-the-open-file-dialogas veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5673">The event monitors whether file-open-from-the-open-filedialog is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5674">Jis taip pat naudojamas mėnesio aktyviems vartotojams / įrenginiams ir debesies patikimumo rodikliams apskaičiuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5674">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5675">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5675">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5676">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – nurodo, ar įvykyje galima tinkamai užpildyti kitų dokumentų telemetrijos susijusias reikšmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5676">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5677">Naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5677">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5678">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – baitų (suglaudintų), kurie, kaip manoma, gali atidaryti failą, skaičius, nepaisant, ar mes juos gausime iki tol, kol vartotojas nori pradėti redaguoti arba galbūt įrašyti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5678">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5679">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – baitų (suglaudintų), kuriuos naudodami galėtume atidaryti failą, skaičius, tačiau norint, kad tai įvyktų, reikės daug investuoti į kodą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5679">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5680">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – baitų (suglaudintų) skaičius, kuriuos privalome turėti prieš pradėdami atidaryti failą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5680">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5681">**Data_BytesUnknown** – baitų skaičius dokumento dalyse, kurių nesitikėjome rasti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5681">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5682">**Data_DetachedDuration** – nurodo, kiek laiko gijoje nebuvo veiklos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5682">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5683">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – nurodo, ar dokumentas yra skirtas tik skaityti, ar redaguojamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5683">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5684">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – iš anksto nustatytų dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežasčių reikšmių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5684">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5685">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5685">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5686">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – elementai, naudojami nuosekliam dokumento atidarymui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5686">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5687">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – dokumentui taikomas elektroninių duomenų apsaugos parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5687">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5688">**Data_Doc_Ext** – dokumento plėtinys (docx, xlsb, pptx ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5688">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5689">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – failo formato protokolo versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5689">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5690">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – „OneDrive“ arba „SharePoint“ interneto domeno vardas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5690">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5691">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – kliento identifikuojamo domeno vardo vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5691">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5692">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – vartotojo tapatybės, naudojamos atidarymui, vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5692">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5693">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – įrašo, kaip dokumentas buvo atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5693">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5694">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – informuoja apie į talpyklą įtrauktas žymes, naudotas nustatyti užklausos parinktis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5694">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5695">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – veiksmai, leidžiami elektroninių duomenų apsaugos strategijos, kuri buvo taikyta dokumentui arba vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5695">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5696">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – žymė, nurodanti, kad dokumentas buvo palaipsniui atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5696">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5697">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – žymė nurodanti, kad dokumentą palaiko bendradarbiavimo tarnyba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5697">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5698">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – žymė, nurodanti, kad atidaryta autonominė dokumento kopija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5698">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5699">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – žymė, nurodanti, kad automatiškai sinchronizuota dokumento kopija yra kompiuteryje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5699">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5700">**Data_Doc_Location** – nurodo tarnybą, pateikusią dokumentą („OneDrive“, „File Server“, „SharePoint“ ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5700">**Data_Doc_Location** - Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5701">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** – nurodo įrenginyje saugomo dokumento žinomą aplanką</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5701">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** - Indicates which Known Folder provided a locally stored document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5702">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** – skaičiuoja bendro redagavimo seanso metu bendradarbiaujančių vartotojų skaičių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5702">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** - Count of the number of fellow users in a collaborative editing session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5703">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** – nurodo, ar nustatytas skaitymo arba skaitymo / rašymo slaptažodžio žymių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5703">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** - Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5704">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – dokumento atidarymo tik kaip skaitomo priežastys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5704">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5705">**Data.Doc.ResourceIdHash** – anonimiškai pateiktų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5705">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - An anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5706">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – nurodo, kaip buvo nustatytas realaus laiko kanalas (RTC) dabartiniam failui (išjungtas, nepalaikomas, pagal pageidavimą, visada įjungta, ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5706">**Data_Doc_RtcType** -  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5707">**Data.Doc.ServerDocId** – nekintamų anonimiškai pateiktų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5707">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - An immutable anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5708">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – protokolo versija, naudojama norint susisiekti su tarnyba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5708">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - the protocol version used to communicate with the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5709">**Data.Doc.ServerType** – tarnybą siūlančio serverio tipas („SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, WOPI ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5709">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - the type of the server offering the service (SharePoint, OneDrive, WOPI, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5710">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – serverio versija, siūlanti tarnybą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5710">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - the server version offering the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5711">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – nustato konkretų dokumentų redagavimo seansą visame seanse</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5711">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - Identifies a specific document edit session within the full session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5712">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – „SharePoint Online“ užklausų diagnostinė informacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5712">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - Diagnostic information from SharePoint Online requests</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5713">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – dokumento dydžio indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5713">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - Indicator of document size</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5714">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – dokumento URL arba kelio specialiųjų simbolių indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5714">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - Indicator of special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5715">**Data_Doc_StreamAvailability** – indikatorius, nurodantis, ar dokumentų srautas yra pasiekiamas arba išjungtas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5715">**Data_Doc_StreamAvailability** - Indicator if document stream is available/disabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5716">**Data_Doc_SyncBackedType** – dokumento tipo indikatorius (vietinis arba pagrįstas tarnyba)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5716">**Data_Doc_SyncBackedType** - Indicator as to the type of document (local or service based)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5717">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – vienpusė maiša, skirta „naïve“ dokumento identifikatoriui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5717">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - One-way hash to create a naïve document identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5718">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** – pirmojo redaktoriaus, dėl kurio buvo išjungtas pervardijimas, identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5718">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** - Identifier of the first editor that caused for rename to be disabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5719">**Data_EditorsCount** – dokumento redaktorių skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5719">**Data_EditorsCount** - Number of editors in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5720">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** – sveikasis skaičius, nurodantis priežastį, kodėl failas buvo priverstinai atidarytas skaitymo / rašymo režimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5720">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** - Integer value representing the reason why the file was forced into read/write mode</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5721">**Data_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure** – nurodo, kad atidaryti pavyko pašalinus triktį, įvykusią atidarant dokumentą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5721">**Data_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure** - Indicates that open succeeded after repairing a failure while opening the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5722">**Data_LastLoggedTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo žymės vieta, naudojama nustatyti, kada dukart nepavyksta bandymas įrašyti (naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5722">**Data_LastLoggedTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify when we fail to try the save twice (used for data quality diagnostics)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5784">**Data\_Data\_Narrator -** Nurodo, ar Diktorius veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5784">**Data\_Data\_Narrator -** indicates if Narrator was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5785">**Data\_Data\_Narrator -** Nurodo, ar Diktorius veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5785">**Data\_Data\_NVDA -** indicates if NVDA was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5786">**Data\_Data\_SA -** Nurodo, ar SA veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5786">**Data\_Data\_SA -** indicates if SA was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5787">**Data\_Data\_Supernova -** Nurodo, ar „Supernova“ veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5787">**Data\_Data\_Supernova -** indicates if Supernova was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5788">**Data\_Data\_SuperNovaessSuite -** Nurodo, ar „SuperNovaAccessSuite“ veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5788">**Data\_Data\_SuperNovaessSuite -** indicates if SuperNovaAccessSuite was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5789">**Data\_Data\_WinEyes -** Nurodo, ar „WinEyes“ veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5789">**Data\_Data\_WinEyes -** indicates if WinEyes was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5790">**Data\_Data\_ZoomText -** Nurodo, ar Teksto mastelis veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5790">**Data\_Data\_ZoomText -** indicates if ZoomText was running during the session</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_darkmode"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5791">Office_Apple_DarkMode</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5791">Office_Apple_DarkMode</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5792">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5792">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5793">Įvykis praneša mums, ar vartotojas naudoja sistemą režime „DarkMode“ ir ar vartotojas perrašė programos „Office“ sistemos „DarkMode“ parametrus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5793">The event tells us if user is running a System on DarkMode and whether the user overwrote the DarkMode System setting in Office.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5794">Naudojame šį įvykį, kad užtikrintume pritaikymą neįgaliesiems ir nustatytume prioritetu vartotojų patirties optimizavimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5794">We use this event to help ensure accessibility and prioritize user-experience optimization.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5795">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5795">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5796">**Data_DarkModeIsEnabled** – nurodo, ar sistemoje įgalintas „DarkMode“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5796">**Data_DarkModeIsEnabled** - Whether DarkMode is enabled in the system.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5797">**Data_RequiresAquaSystemAppearanceEnabled** – ar programoje „Office“ perrašytas „DarkMode“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5797">**Data_RequiresAquaSystemAppearanceEnabled** - Whether DarkMode is overwritten in Office.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_hardwarekeyboardinuse_apple"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5798">Office_Apple_HardwareKeyboardInUse_Apple</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5798">Office_Apple_HardwareKeyboardInUse_Apple</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5799">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5799">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5800">Įvykis praneša mums, kad vartotojas prijungia klaviatūrą prie savo mobiliojo įrenginio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5800">The event tells us that a user is attaching a keyboard to their mobile device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5801">Įvykis padeda patobulinti pritaikymą neįgaliesiems ir optimizuoti mūsų vartotojų patirtį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5801">The event helps us improve accessibility and optimize our user experience.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5802">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5802">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5803">**Data_CollectionTime** – laiko žyma, rodanti įvykio rinkimo laiką.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5803">**Data_CollectionTime** - A timestamp denoting the event collection time.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5846">Šis įvykis nurodo vartotojo arba sistemos inicijuotą veiksmą, kuris yra „Office“ vartotojo privatumo funkcijų dalis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5846">This event represents a user or system initiated action that is part of the privacy User experience for Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5847">Jis suaktyvinamas privatumo pirmojo paleidimo dialogo languose, paskyros privatumo dialogo lange ir privatumo pranešimuose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5847">It is triggered on the privacy First Run dialogs, Account Privacy dialog, and privacy notifications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5848">Šis įvykis naudojamas norint suprasti: vartotojus, sutinkančius su „Office“ privatumo parametrais, vartotojus, keičiančius „Office“ privatumo parametrus, ir „Office“ privatumo parametrus, kurie atnaujinami vartotojo seansuose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5848">The event is used to understand the following: users consenting to Office privacy settings, users changing Office privacy settings, and Office privacy settings getting updated in user sessions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5849">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5849">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5850">**Data_ActionId –** vartotojo veiksmas privatumo dialogo lange</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5850">**Data_ActionId -** User action in a privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5851">**Data_ControllerConnectedServicesState –** papildomų pasirinktinių prijungtųjų funkcijų vartotojo strategijos parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5851">**Data_ControllerConnectedServicesState -** User policy setting for additional optional connected experiences</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5852">**Data_DownloadedContentServiceGroupState –** atsisiųsto turinio vartotojo parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5852">**Data_DownloadedContentServiceGroupState -** User setting for downloaded content</span></span> 
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5853">**Data_ForwardLinkId –** saitas į vartotojo scenarijaus privatumo dokumentaciją</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5853">**Data_ForwardLinkId -** Link to privacy documentation for the user scenario</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5854">**Data_HRESULT –** klaidų, įvykusių sąveikos su privatumo dialogo langu metu, įrašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5854">**Data_HRESULT -** Record of errors during interaction with a privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5855">**Data_IsEnterpriseUser –** vartotojo licencijos kategorija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5855">**Data_IsEnterpriseUser -** User license category</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5856">**Data_OfficeServiceConnectionState –** prijungtų tarnybų vartotojo parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5856">**Data_OfficeServiceConnectionState -** User setting for connected services</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5857">**Data_RecordRegistry –** įmonės privatumo dialogo lango rodymo įrašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5857">**Data_RecordRegistry -** Record of showing the enterprise privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5858">**Data_Scenario –** pirmojo paleidimo scenarijus pagal vartotojo licenciją ir kategoriją</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5858">**Data_Scenario -** First run scenario based on the user license and category</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5859">**Data_SeenInsidersDialog –** „Insider“ privatumo dialogo lango rodymo įrašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5859">**Data_SeenInsidersDialog -** Record of showing the Insiders privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5860">**Data_SendTelemetryOption –** telemetrijai skirtas vartotojo parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5860">**Data_SendTelemetryOption -** User setting for telemetry</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5861">**Data_SendTelemetryOptionPolicy –** telemetrijai skirtas vartotojo strategijos parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5861">**Data_SendTelemetryOptionPolicy -** User policy setting for telemetry</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5862">**Data_UserCategory –** vartotojo paskyros tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5862">**Data_UserCategory -** User account type</span></span>  

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5863">**Data_UserCCSDisabled –** papildomų pasirinktinių prisijungtųjų funkcijų vartotojo nepaisymas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5863">**Data_UserCCSDisabled -** User override for additional optional connected experiences</span></span>

   - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5864">**Data_UserContentServiceGroupState –** vartotojo parametrai, skirti turiniui analizuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5864">**Data_UserContentServiceGroupState -** User setting for analyzing content</span></span>

## <a name="product-and-service-performance-data-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-5866">Produktų ir tarnybų našumo duomenų įvykiai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-5866">Product and service performance data events</span></span>
