#### <a name="json_parse_error"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6375">json_parse_error</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6375">json_parse_error</span></span> 
 
<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6376">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad klaidą pateikė json formato analizatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6376">This event denotes that an error is thrown by the json parser.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6377">Galėsime derinti nuskaitytą registro eilutę, kuri buvo išsiųsta json formato analizatoriui, kad būtų galima užtikrinti sklandžią mūsų vartotojų patirtį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6377">We will be able to debug the read registry string that was sent to the json parser, to allow a smooth experience for our users.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6378">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6378">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6379">**Error** – šis parametras susideda iš klaidos pranešimo, grąžinto klaidos objekto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6379">**Error** - This consists of the error message that the error object returns.</span></span>

#### <a name="mail_filter_component"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6380">mail_filter_component</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6380">mail_filter_component</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6381">Šis įvykis leidžia aptikti ir išspręsti problemas, kurios gali trikdyti laiškų filtravimo patirtį ir gali būti neįkeliami ar netinkamai rodomi filtrai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6381">This event lets us detect and fix issues where there is perceivable performance impact on your mail filtering experience which would cause your filters to not load or display properly.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6382">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6382">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6383">**above_40fps** – kadrų skaičius virš 40 fps</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6383">**above_40fps** - count of frames rendered above 40fps</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6384">**above_50fps** – kadrų skaičius virš 50 fps</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6384">**above_50fps** - count of frames rendered above 50fps</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6385">**above_55fps** – kadrų skaičius virš 55 fps</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6385">**above_55fps** - count of frames rendered above 55fps</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6386">**account_counter** – kiekvieno įrenginyje esančio paskyros tipo skaičius, pvz., „Office 365“ paskyra = 1 paskyra, „Outlook.com“ paskyra = 1 paskyra.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6386">**account_counter** - count of each account type present on the device, for example, an Office 365 account = 1 account, Outlook.com account = 1 account.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6387">**ad_not_shown_reason** – priežastis, kodėl nerodomi skelbimai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6387">**ad_not_shown_reason** - reason why ads are not being shown</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6388">**ad_shown** – ar skelbimas buvo rodomas (jei įjungti skelbimai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6388">**ad_shown** - whether an add was shown (if ads enabled)</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6389">**age** – asmens amžius (naudojamas patvirtinti skelbimų amžiaus apribojimų atitiktį)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6389">**age** - age of the person (used to confirm compliance with age limitations on ads)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6390">**app_instance** – „Outlook“ yra 2 „Duo“ įvesties taškai, vienas – kalendoriui, o kitas – paštui. Abu gali būti paleisti greta kelių egzempliorių aplinkoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6390">**app_instance** – Outlook has 2 entry points for Duo, one is for Calendar and one is for Mail and both can be launched side by side in multi instance environment.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6391">Tai praneš mums, kuris egzempliorius pateiks šį pranešimą: pašto arba kalendoriaus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6391">This will let us know which instance is making this reporting call, either Mail or Calendar</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6392">**component_name** – filtruojant aktyvaus komponento/rodinio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6392">**component_name** - the name of the component/view which is active during the filtering</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6393">**folder_type** – filtruojamo aplanko tipas (pvz., Gauta, Šiukšliadėžė, ne sistemos)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6393">**folder_type** - the type of folder which is being filtered (e.g. Inbox, Trash, NonSystem)</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6394">**has_hx** – ar įrenginys turi bent vieną HX (nauja el. pašto sinchronizavimo tarnyba) paskyrą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6394">**has_hx** - whether the device has at least one Hx (the new email syncing service) account</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6395">**has_subscription** – ar įrenginys turi skelbimų prenumeratą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6395">**has_subscription** - whether the device has an ads subscription</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6396">**is_all_accounts_inbox** – ar dabartinis aplankas Gauta yra aplankas „visos paskyros“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6396">**is_all_accounts_inbox** - whether the current inbox is the "all accounts" folder</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6397">**is_current_account** – ar dabartinė aktyvi paskyra yra skelbimų paskyra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6397">**is_current_account** - whether the current active account is the ads account</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6398">**load_error_code** – klaidos kodas įkeliant skelbimus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6398">**load_error_code** - error code when loading ads</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6399">**network_error_code** – tinklo klaidos kodas, kai prašoma skelbimų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6399">**network_error_code** - network error code when requesting ads</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6400">**orientation** – ekrano padėtis įvykio metu (stačias arba gulsčias)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6400">**orientation** - the screen orientation at the time of the even (portrait or landscape)</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6401">**sub_error_type** – išsamus klaidos tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6401">**sub_error_type** - detailed error type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6402">**taskId** – „TaskId“ pateiks mums dabartinio egzemplioriaus „taskId“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6402">**taskId** – TaskId will give us the current instance’s taskId.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6403">Tai bus reikalinga kelių egzempliorių aplinkoje, jei vartotojas nori paleisti tuos pačius egzempliorius (kalendorius, kalendorius arba paštas, paštas) greta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6403">This will be required in multi instance environment if user wants to launch same instances (Calendar, Calendar or Mail, Mail) side by side</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6404">**total_count** – bendras rodomų kadrų skaičius pagal komponentą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6404">**total_count** - total frames displayed by the component</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6405">**view_duration** – kiek laiko vartotojas peržiūrėjo komponentą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6405">**view_duration** - how long the component was viewed by the user</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidofficelaunchtolandingpagelatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6406">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeLaunchToLandingPageLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6406">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeLaunchToLandingPageLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6407">Svarbu užfiksuoti programos veikimo metriką, atsižvelgiant į taikomosios programos atsakymo laiką nuo paleidimo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6407">Critical to capture for app performance metric with respect to the response time of the app from the boot.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6408">„Microsoft“ šią funkciją naudoja fiksuoti laiką, skirtą taikomajai programai reaguoti ir aptikti scenarijus, kurie gali veikti paleidimo laiką programose „Word“, „Excel“ ar „PowerPoint“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6408">Microsoft uses this to collect the time taken for the app to be responsive and also detect scenarios that may impact boot time in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6409">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6409">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6410">**AnyCrashInteractionDuringBoot** – Bulio logika bet kokiam gedimui, kuris įvyko paleidimo metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6410">**AnyCrashInteractionDuringBoot** - Boolean for any crash encountered during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6411">**AppActivationTimeInMs** – taikomosios programos etapo laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6411">**AppActivationTimeInMs** - App phase time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6412">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** – Bulio logika taikomosios programos sustabdymui paleidimo metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6412">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** - Boolean for app suspension during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6413">**AvailableMemoryInMB** – pasiekiama atmintis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6413">**AvailableMemoryInMB** - available memory</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6414">**CollectionTime** – įvykio laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6414">**CollectionTime** - time of event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6415">**DalvikHeapLimitInMB** – netvarkiojo masyvo informacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6415">**DalvikHeapLimitInMB** - Heap info</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6416">**DocumentRecoveryInvoked** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar buvo atkurtas koks nors dokumentas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6416">**DocumentRecoveryInvoked** - Boolean to indicate if any document was recovered</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6417">**ExtractionDone** – vietinės bibliotekos išskleidimo laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6417">**ExtractionDone** - Native library extraction time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6418">**FastBootGainTimeInMs** – greito paleidimo užbaigimui skirtas laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6418">**FastBootGainTimeInMs** - Time for fast boot completion</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6419">**FileActivationAttempted** – Bulio logika, rodanti, ar aktyvinus failą taikomoji programa buvo paleista</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6419">**FileActivationAttempted** - Boolean to indicate if app was launched due to File activation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6420">**HasLogcatLoggingImpactOnBoot** – Bulio logika, rodanti, ar „logcat“ paveikė paleidimo laiką</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6420">**HasLogcatLoggingImpactOnBoot** - Boolean to indicate if logcat impacted boot time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6421">**IsThisFirstLaunch** – Bulio logika, rodanti, ar tai yra pirmasis taikomosios programos paleidimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6421">**IsThisFirstLaunch** - Boolean to indicate if this is first app launch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6422">**LatencyTimeInMilliSec** – gaištis milisekundėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6422">**LatencyTimeInMilliSec** - latency in millisecond</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6423">**LibrarySharingTimeInMs** – bibliotekų bendrinimui skirtas laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6423">**LibrarySharingTimeInMs** - time for sharing libraries</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6424">**LoadMinLibsTimeInMs** – minimalus bibliotekų rinkinio įkėlimo laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6424">**LoadMinLibsTimeInMs** - Loading time for the minimum set of libraries</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6425">**MruListingTimeInMs** - MRU įkėlimo laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6425">**MruListingTimeInMs** - time to load MRU</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6426">**NativeLibrariesLoadTime** – CPP bibliotekos įkėlimo laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6426">**NativeLibrariesLoadTime** - CPP library load time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6427">**NumberOfRunningProcesses** – vykdomų procesų skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6427">**NumberOfRunningProcesses** - number of running processes</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6428">**NumberOfRunningProcesses** – vykdomų procesų skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6428">**NumberOfRunningProcesses** - Number of running processes</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6429">**NumberOfRunningServices** – veikiančių tarnybų skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6429">**NumberOfRunningServices** - Number of running services</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6430">**OfficeActivityTimeInMs** – OfficeActivity inicijavimo laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6430">**OfficeActivityTimeInMs** - Time for initing OfficeActivity</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6431">**PostAppInitTimeInMs** – taikomosios programos etapo laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6431">**PostAppInitTimeInMs** - app phase time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6432">**PreAppInitializationTime** – taikomosios programos etapo inicijavimo laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6432">**PreAppInitializationTime** - App phase init time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6433">**PreAppInitTimeInMs** – taikomosios programos etapo laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6433">**PreAppInitTimeInMs** - app phase time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6434">**TotalMemoryInMB** – bendra atmintis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6434">**TotalMemoryInMB** - total memory</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6435">**UIRaaSDownloadLanguagePackageBoot** – informacija, susijusi su kalbos paketo atsisiuntimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6435">**UIRaaSDownloadLanguagePackageBoot** - information related to language pack download</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6436">**UserDialogInterruptionDuringBoot** – Bulio logika bet kokiam blokavimo dialogo langui, rodomam paleidimo metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6436">**UserDialogInterruptionDuringBoot** - Boolean for any blocking dialog shown during boot</span></span>


#### <a name="office_apple_apple_appboot_mac"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6437">Office_Apple_Apple_AppBoot_Mac</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6437">Office_Apple_Apple_AppBoot_Mac</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6438">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6438">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6439">Įvykis naudojamas skaičiuoti taikomosios programos paleidimo laikui, taip pat gauti tam tikrą informaciją apie įkrovos tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6439">The event is used to collect the time taken to boot the app, as well as some details on the type of boot done.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6440">Šis įvykis padeda mums stebėti savo našumą ir teikti produktyvumo patobulinimų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6440">This event helps us monitor our performance and provide performance improvements.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6441">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6441">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6442">**Data_ Data_EvtBootTimerDocStageReady** – laikas reikalingas pasiekti tam tikrą kodo vietą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6442">**Data_ Data_EvtBootTimerDocStageReady** - Time elapsed until reaching certain point in code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6443">**Data_DocumentRecoveryInvoked** – nurodo, ar dokumento atkūrimas buvo iškviestas paleidimo metu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6443">**Data_DocumentRecoveryInvoked** - Whether document recovery was invoked during boot.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6444">**Data_EvtBootTimerBootIdle** – laikas reikalingas pasiekti tam tikrą kodo vietą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6444">**Data_EvtBootTimerBootIdle** - Time elapsed until reaching certain point in code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6445">**Data_EvtBootTimerFinishLaunchEnd** – laikas reikalingas pasiekti tam tikrą kodo vietą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6445">**Data_EvtBootTimerFinishLaunchEnd** - Time elapsed until reaching certain point in code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6446">**Data_EvtBootTimerLaunchDidFinish** – laikas reikalingas pasiekti tam tikrą kodo vietą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6446">**Data_EvtBootTimerLaunchDidFinish** - Time elapsed until reaching certain point in code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6447">**Data_EvtBootTimerLaunchStart** – laikas reikalingas pasiekti tam tikrą kodo vietą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6447">**Data_EvtBootTimerLaunchStart** - Time elapsed until reaching certain point in code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6448">**Data_EvtBootTimerMainStart** – laikas reikalingas pasiekti tam tikrą kodo vietą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6448">**Data_EvtBootTimerMainStart** - Time elapsed until reaching certain point in code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6449">**Data_EvtBootTimerStaticInit** – laikas reikalingas pasiekti tam tikrą kodo vietą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6449">**Data_EvtBootTimerStaticInit** - Time elapsed until reaching certain point in code.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6535">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6535">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6536">Šis įvykis naudojamas „Office“ taikomųjų programų sveikatai stebėti, taip pat tirti trikčių priežastis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6536">The event is used to monitor the health of our Office applications as well as for investigating causes of failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6537">Renkame informaciją, kiek kartų taikomoji programa neatsakė iki buvo pasirinktas nesklandusis programos išėjimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6537">We collect the number of times an application appeared to be unresponsive prior to hitting an ungraceful application exit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6539">**Data_HangsDetected** – kiek kartų taikomoji programa neatsakė iki buvo pastebėtas nesklandusis programos išėjimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6539">**Data_HangsDetected** - The number of times the application appeared to become unresponsive prior to observing the ungraceful application exit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6540">**Data_LastSessionId** – seanso, kurio metu buvo stebėtas nesklandusis programos išėjimas, identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6540">**Data_LastSessionId** - The identifier for the session in which the ungraceful application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6541">**Data_SessionBuildNumber** – papildoma taikomosios programos versija, kurioje buvo pastebėtas nesklandusis išėjimas iš programos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6541">**Data_SessionBuildNumber** - The minor version of the application in which an ungraceful application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6542">**Data_SessionVersion** – pagrindinė taikomosios programos versija, kurioje buvo pastebėtas nesklandusis išėjimas iš programos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6542">**Data_SessionVersion** - The major version of the application in which an ungraceful application exit was observed.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_whatsnewerrorandwarning"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6543">Office_Apple_WhatsNewErrorAndWarning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6543">Office_Apple_WhatsNewErrorAndWarning</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6544">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6544">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6545">Įvykis naudojamas funkcijos Kas nauja sveikatai stebėti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6545">The event is used to monitor the health of the What's New feature.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6546">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad funkcijos Kas nauja turinio analizavimo įvyko klaida/įspėjimas, nurodanti galimas turinio kūrimo triktis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6546">This event denotes that an error/warning occurred while parsing What's New content, pointing to potential content authoring issues.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6547">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6547">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6548">**Data_ContentKey** – žymiklis, nurodantis turinio dalį, kuri galėjo sukelti klaidą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6548">**Data_ContentKey** - A pointer to the section of the content that is likely to have caused the error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6549">**Data_ErrorCode** – pastebėtos klaidos kodas (jei yra)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6549">**Data_ErrorCode** - The observed error code (if available)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6550">**Data_ErrorDescription** – klaidos aprašas (jei yra)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6550">**Data_ErrorDescription** - A description of the error (if available)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6551">**Data_EventID** – renkame duomenis eilutės, nurodančios pastebėtos klaidos tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6551">**Data_EventID** - We collect a string representing the type of error observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6552">**Data_IncludesHTMLTag** – ar turinyje yra raiškiojo html</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6552">**Data_IncludesHTMLTag** - Whether the content contains rich html</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6553">**Data_IncludesItemsTag** – ar turinyje yra elementų hierarchija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6553">**Data_IncludesItemsTag** - Whether the content contains a hierarchy of items</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6554">**Data_LengthOfRawData** – turinio dydis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6554">**Data_LengthOfRawData** - The size of the content</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6555">**Data_RequestURL** – URL, iš kurio atsisiųstas turinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6555">**Data_RequestURL** - The URL from which the content was downloaded</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6556">**Data_ServerLanguageTag** – kalba, kuria buvo sukurtas turinys.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6556">**Data_ServerLanguageTag** - The language the content was in.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6557">**Data_StatusCode** – klaidos būsena (jei yra)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6557">**Data_StatusCode** - The status of the error (if available)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilityrichapimethodinvocation"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6558">Office.Extensibility.RichApiMethodInvocation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6558">Office.Extensibility.RichApiMethodInvocation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6559">Šis įvykis suaktyvinamas, kai klientas naudoja „Office“ papildinį ir paslaugai teikti iškviečia raiškųjį API.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6559">When customer uses an Office Add-in and calls Rich API for providing service, this event will be triggered.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6560">Naudojamas norint įvertinti paslaugos patikimumą, veikimą ir raiškiojo API metodo naudojimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6560">Used to measure the service reliability, performance and usage for Rich API method invocation.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6561">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6561">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6562">**Api** – visas API pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6562">**Api** - Full name of the API</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6563">**DispFlag** – bitų žymė, aprašanti metodo iškvietimo tipą (pavyzdžiui, 0 x 1 = METHOD, 0 x 2 = PROPERTYGET, 0 x 4 = PROPERTYPUT, 0 x 8 = PROPERTYPUTREF)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6563">**DispFlag** - A bit flag describing the type of method call (Ex: 0x1 = METHOD, 0x2 = PROPERTYGET, 0x4 = PROPERTYPUT, 0x8 = PROPERTYPUTREF)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6564">**DispId** – iškviečiamo metodo išsiuntimo ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6564">**DispId** - Dispatch ID for the method being called</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6565">**HResult** – metodo iškvietimo „HResult“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6565">**HResult** - HResult for the method call</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6566">**Latency** – iškvietimo gaištis mikrosekundėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6566">**Latency** - Latency for the call, in microseconds</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6567">**ReqId** – GUID, skirtas paketo užklausai, kuriai šis metodas priklauso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6567">**ReqId** - GUID for the batch request that this method belongs to</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6568">**TypeId** – GUID, skirtas sąsajai, kuriai šis metodas iškviečiamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6568">**TypeId** - GUID for the interface on which this method being called</span></span>


#### <a name="officemanageabilityserviceapplypolicy"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6569">Office.Manageability.Service.ApplyPolicy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6569">Office.Manageability.Service.ApplyPolicy</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6570">Svarbi telemetrija, skirta gedimams stebėti\\Sėkmingas debesijos strategijos nustatymų registravimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6570">Critical telemetry to track failure\\Success of applying cloud policy settings to registry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6571">„LastError“ nurodo, kodėl ir kur nepavyko taikyti registro strategijos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6571">LastError tells why and where the Application of policy in registry failed.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6573">**Data.ApplyLogMsg** – išimties pranešimas, jei strategija buvo taikoma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6573">**Data.ApplyLogMsg** - The exception msg if any while policy was being applied</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6574">**Data.Cid** – dinamiškai sukurtas sąsajos identifikatorius, siunčiamas į tarnybą, kai buvo atliktas tarnybos iškvietimas, kad gautų debesijos strategiją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6574">**Data.Cid** - dynamically generated correlation identifier sent to the service when the service call was made to fetch the cloud policy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6575">Naudojamas nustatyti, kuris iškvietimas sukėlė problemą taikant strategiją debesyje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6575">Used to correlate which call caused an issue while applying the policies on the cloud.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6576">**Data.Last Error** – Viena iš penkių eilučių reikšmių (surašytuvai), norint užregistruoti, kuris strategijos taikymo etapas buvo įvykdytas, kai įvyko išimtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6576">**Data.Last Error** - One of five string values (enumerators) to log which stage of policy application was being executed when the exception occurred</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6578">Šis kritinis signalas naudojamas siekiant užtikrinti, kad vartotojui prisijungus prie „OneNote“ „Android“ programos, bloknotai būtų tinkamai parengti ir juos būtų galima sėkmingai pasiekti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6578">The critical signal used to ensure that after a user signs-into a OneNote Android App, notebooks are properly provisioned so that they can be easily accessed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6579">Tai naudojama siekiant užtikrinti regresijos aptikimą, kuris ypač svarbus programai „OneNote“ ir tarnybos sveikatai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6579">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6580">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6580">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6581">**AppSuspendedDuringEvent** – pateikia Bulio logiką, kad būtų galima nurodyti, ar programa buvo laikinai sustabdyta pateikimo metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6581">**AppSuspendedDuringEvent**: Returns boolean to indicate if app was suspended during provisioning</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6582">**Klaidos kodas** – pateikia klaidos kodą, atsakingą už parengimo triktis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6582">**ErrorCode** – Returns the error code responsible for failure of provisioning</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6583">**NetworkConnection** – naudojamo įrenginio tinklo ryšio tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6583">**NetworkConnection**: The type of network connectivity of the device in use</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6584">**NetworkDataExchange** – įrašo baitų skaičių, kuriais buvo apsikeista pateikiant.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6584">**NetworkDataExchange** - Records the number of bytes exchanged during provisioning.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6585">**ServerType** – pateikia serverio, siūlančio tarnybą, tipą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6585">**ServerType**: Returns the type of the server offering the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6586">**TimeTakenInMilliSeconds** – pateikia laiką, kiek truko visas pateikimas milisekundėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6586">**TimeTakenInMilliSeconds**: Returns time taken to complete provisioning in millisecond</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6602">**ShowChooseProfileDlg** – Ar buvo rodomas dialogo langas Pasirinkti profilį</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6602">**ShowChooseProfileDlg** – Whether the Choose Profile Dialog was shown</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookmacperformanceunresponsive"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6615">Office.Outlook.Mac.PerformanceUnresponsive</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6615">Office.Outlook.Mac.PerformanceUnresponsive</span></span>

#### <a name="officeperformanceboot"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6620">Office.Performance.Boot</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6620">Office.Performance.Boot</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6621">Surinkta taikomosios programos „Office“ paleidimo metu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6621">Collected when an Office application is booted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6622">Nurodoma, ar paleidimas buvo pradėtas atidarant failą, ar paleidžiant per meniu Pradžia, ar tai buvo pirmasis taikomosios programos paleidimas, kiek atminties naudoja taikomoji programa, ir ar vartotojui buvo parodyta blokuojama vartotojo sąsaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6622">Includes whether the boot was initiated by opening a file or launching via the Start menu, whether this was the first boot of the application, how much memory the application is using, and whether there was any blocking UI shown to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6623">Naudojama išmatuoti, kaip greitai veikia taikomosios programos „Office“ paleidimas ir kiek atminties naudojama paleidimo metu, kad užtikrinti priimtiną vartotojo patirtį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6623">Used to measure how fast Office applications boot and how much memory they use when they start, to ensure there is an acceptable user experience.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6624">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6624">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6625">**ActivationKind** – ar taikomoji programa buvo pradėta naudojant Pradžios meniu, atidarant failą arba naudojant OLE automatizavimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6625">**ActivationKind** - Whether the application was started by launching from the Start menu, by opening a file, or through OLE Automation.</span></span>
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6626">**BootToStart** – ar paleidžiant šią taikomąją programą vartotojas pasirinko rodyti pradžios ekraną.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6626">**BootToStart** - Whether the user has chosen to show the start screen when this application starts.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6627">**ColdBoot** – ar „Office“ taikomoji programa paleidžiama pirmą kartą paleidus sistemą iš naujo, ar reikėjo programos dvejetainį įkelti iš disko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6627">**ColdBoot** - Whether is first time Office application runs after a system restart or application binary had to be loaded from disk.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6628">**Model** – įrenginio modelis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6628">**DeviceModel** - The model of the device.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6629">\*\*\*\* – atidarant dokumentą nurodo dokumentą pateikusią tarnybą („OneDrive“, „File Server“, „SharePoint“ ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6629">**DocLocation** -  When opening a document, indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6630">**DurationUntilMso20Initialization** – trukmė mikrosekundėmis nuo „Office“ proceso pradžios iki mso20win32client.dll įkėlimo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6630">**DurationUntilMso20Initialization** - The duration in microseconds it took between when the Office process was initialized and mso20win32client.dll was loaded.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6631">**FirstBoot** – ar tai buvo pirmas taikomosios programos įkrovimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6631">**FirstBoot** - Whether this was a first boot of the application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6632">**Initializationduration** – pirmojo „Office“ inicijavimo proceso trukmė mikrosekundėmis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6632">**InitializationDuration** - The duration in microseconds it took to first initialize the Office process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6633">**InterruptionMessageId** – ar paleidimas buvo pertrauktas dialogo lango, prašančio naudotojo atlikti įvestį, dialogo lango ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6633">**InterruptionMessageId** - If the boot was interrupted by a dialog asking for user input, the ID of the dialog.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6634">**TotalWorkingSetMB** – proceso darbinio rinkinio atminties kiekis megabaitais.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6634">**TotalWorkingSetMB** - The amount of memory in megabytes in the process's working set.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6635">**VirtualSetMB** – proceso virtualiojo rinkinio atminties kiekis megabaitais.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6635">**VirtualSetMB** - The amount of memory in megabytes in the process's virtual set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6636">(tik „MacOS“/ „iOS“)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6636">(MacOS / iOS only)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6637">**WorkingSetPeakMB** – didžiausias atminties kiekis megabaitais, kuris iki šiol yra buvęs proceso darbiniame rinkinyje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6637">**WorkingSetPeakMB** - The largest amount of memory in megabytes that was ever in the process's working set so far.</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointrehearsalsessionmetrics"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6671">Office.PowerPoint.Rehearsal.SessionMetrics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6671">Office.PowerPoint.Rehearsal.SessionMetrics</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6672">Įvykis paleidžiamas, kai kalbėjimo seansas sustabdomas pranešėjo pagalbinei priemonei.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6672">Event triggered when the speech session is stopped for Presenter Coach.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6673">Šis įvykis padeda mums užfiksuoti kai kurią metriką repeticijos seanse pranešėjo pagalbinėje priemonėje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6673">This event helps us in capturing some metrics for a rehearsal session in Presenter Coach.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6674">Tai padės išlaikyti aukštą paslaugos kokybę šiai funkcijai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6674">It will help in maintaining a high quality of service for this feature.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6675">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6675">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6676">**AuthDurationInMs** – tai yra laikas milisekundėmis, kai naudojamas autentifikavimas (atnaujinti autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6676">**AuthDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds for authentication (refresh the auth token).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6677">**AuthError** – tai aprašo įvyko autentifikavimo klaidą (jei įvyko).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6677">**AuthError** – This describes the authentication error that occurred (if at all).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6678">**AvgFragmentLatencyInMs** – tai vidutinis tinklo kalbos pranešimų kelionės pirmyn ir atgal laikas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6678">**AvgFragmentLatencyInMs** – This is the average round-trip time for network speech messages.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6679">**ConnectDurationInMs** – tai laikas, kai seansas baigs jungimąsi per milisekundes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6679">**ConnectDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds for the session to complete the connection.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6680">**FirstAudioDelayInMs** – tai laikas, per kurį turi būti gaunami pirmieji garsiniai duomenys.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6680">**FirstAudioDelayInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds for the first audio data to be received.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6681">**InitMediaCaptureLayerDurationInMs** – tai laikas, per kurį turi būti inicijuotas medijos/garso fiksavimo sluoksnio inicijavimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6681">**InitMediaCaptureLayerDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to initialise the media/audio capture layer.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6682">**LocallyDroppedMessageCount** – tai bendras pranešimų, kurie buvo išmesti vietoje, skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6682">**LocallyDroppedMessageCount** – This is the total number of messages dropped locally.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6683">**OpenFrontDoorConnectionDurationInMs** – tai laikas milisekundėmis, kuris buvo paimtas norint atidaryti ryšį su „FrontDoor“ tarnyba.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6683">**OpenFrontDoorConnectionDurationInMs** – This is the time in milliseconds taken to open the connection to the FrontDoor service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6684">**SendAdaptationTextDurationInMs** – tai laikas, kai į tarnybą siunčiamas adaptacijos tekstas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6684">**SendAdaptationTextDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to send the adaptation text to the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6685">**ServiceDroppedMessageCount** – tai bendras tarnybos išmestų pranešimų skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6685">**ServiceDroppedMessageCount** – This is the total number of messages dropped by the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6686">**SessionId** – tai kalbos „Frontdoor“ seanso ID. Galime jį naudoti, kad galėtumėte derinti paslaugų žurnalus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6686">**SessionId** – This is the speech frontdoor session id. We can use this to debug service logs.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6687">**SpeechClientResultEventsWithTimestamps** – tai klaidų kodų, gautų kartu su laiko ženklais, kurie gali padėti taisyti, masyvas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6687">**SpeechClientResultEventsWithTimestamps** – This is an array of error codes received along with the timestamps which can help in debugging.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6688">**SpeechHResultsWithTimestamps** – tai klaidų kodų, gautų kartu su laiko ženklais, kurie gali padėti atlikti derinimą, masyvas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6688">**SpeechHResultsWithTimestamps** – This is an array of error codes received along with the timestamps which can help in debugging.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6689">**StartSpeechCaptureDurationInMs** – tai laikas milisekundėmis, kol pradedama kalbėjimo fiksavimo funkcija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6689">**StartSpeechCaptureDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to start speech capture.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6690">**TotalMessageCount** – tai bendras į tarnybą siunčiamų garsinių pranešimų skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6690">**TotalMessageCount** – This is the total number of audio messages sent to the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6691">**WebSocketConnectDurationInMs** – tai laikas, kai reikia baigti naudoti interneto lizdą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6691">**WebSocketConnectDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to complete the web socket connection.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeuxofficeinsiderregistercurrentinsider"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6699">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.RegisterCurrentInsider</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6699">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.RegisterCurrentInsider</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6700">Kritinis signalas, skirtas stebėti sėkmingą arba nesėkmingą vartotojų, kurie anksčiau nebuvo užregistruoti kaip „Office Insider“ programos dalyviai, registravimą naudojant „Office Insider“ komponavimo versijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6700">Critical signal for tracking success or failure of registering users using Office Insider builds who weren't registered as Office Insiders before.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6701">Jis visų pirma taikomas dabartiniams „Office Insider“ programos dalyviams, kurie prie „Office Insider“ programos prisijungė prieš įtraukiant „Office Insider“ programos dalyvių registraciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6701">Main scenario for this is current Office Insiders who joined Office Insider program before registration of Office Insiders was added.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6702">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6702">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6703">**Data_RegisterInsider** – „Office Insider“ registracijos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6703">**Data_RegisterInsider** - Status of Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6704">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** – „Office Insider“ registracijos rezultatų kodas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6704">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** - Result code for Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6705">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** – dabartinė registracijos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6705">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** - Current registration state</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6706">**Data_RegistrationStateDesired** – prašoma registracijos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6706">**Data_RegistrationStateDesired** - Requested registration state</span></span>


#### <a name="officeuxofficeinsidershowofficeinsiderdlg"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6707">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.ShowOfficeInsiderDlg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6707">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.ShowOfficeInsiderDlg</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6708">Kritinis signalas, naudojamas vartotojo sąveikai su dialogu „Prisijunkite prie „Office Insider“ stebėti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6708">Critical signal tracking user interaction with Join Office Insider dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6709">Jis naudojamas nustatyti bet kokioms problemoms, kurios kyla vykdant vartotojo inicijuotus pakeitimus, tokius kaip prisijungimas prie „Office Insider“ programos, pasitraukimas iš jos arba „Office Insider“ programos dalyvio lygio pakeitimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6709">It is used for identifying any issues in performing user-initiated changes such as joining or leaving Office Insider program and changing Office Insider level.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6710">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6710">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6711">**Data_AcceptedContactMeNew** – nurodo, ar vartotojas sutiko, kad prisijungus prie „Office Insider“ programos, „Microsoft“ su juo susisiektų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6711">**Data_AcceptedContactMeNew** - Indicates if a user has accepted to be contacted by Microsoft upon joining Office Insider program</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6712">**Data_InsiderLevel** – „Insider“ lygis atidarant dialogo langą „Prisijunkite prie „Office Insider“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6712">**Data_InsiderLevel** - Insider Level on opening of "Join Office Insider" dialog</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6713">**Data_InsiderLevelNew** – „Insider“ lygis uždarant dialogo langą „Prisijunkite prie „Office Insider“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6713">**Data_InsiderLevelNew** - Insider level on closing of "Join Office Insider" dialog</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6714">**Data_IsInternalUser** – nurodo, ar taikomoji programa vykdoma naudojant „Microsoft“ įmonės paskyros kredencialus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6714">**Data_IsInternalUser** - Indicates whether the application runs under the credentials of a Microsoft corporate account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6715">**Data_IsInternalUser** – nurodo, ar kodas gali nustatyti, ar taikomoji programa vykdoma naudojant „Microsoft“ įmonės paskyros kredencialus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6715">**Data_IsInternalUserInit** - Indicates whether the code could determine whether the application runs under the credentials of a Microsoft corporate account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6716">**Data_OpenNewsletterWebpage** – nurodo, ar „Office Insider“ informacinio biuletenio prenumeratos saitas buvo paspaustas su sąlyga, kad vartotojas prisijungė prie „„Office Insider“ programos, naujienlaiškio prenumeratos funkcija įjungta ir vartotojas neatšaukė „Office Insider“ naujienlaiškio prenumeratos svetainės atidarymo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6716">**Data_OpenNewsletterWebpage** - Indicates whether Office Insider Newsletter Subscription link was triggered under condition that user has joined Office Insider program, Newsletter Subscription feature is enabled, and the user have not canceled opening of Office Insider Newsletter Subscription webpage.</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6717">**Data_RegisterInsider** – „Office Insider“ registracijos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6717">**Data_RegisterInsider** - Status of Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6718">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** – „Office Insider“ registracijos rezultatų kodas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6718">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** - Result code for Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6719">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** – dabartinė registracijos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6719">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** - Current registration state</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6720">**Data_RegistrationStateDesired** – prašoma registracijos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6720">**Data_RegistrationStateDesired** - Requested registration state</span></span>


#### <a name="officevisiosharedvisiofilerender"></a><span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6721">Office.Visio.Shared.VisioFileRender</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6721">Office.Visio.Shared.VisioFileRender</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6722">Šis įvykis užfiksuoja failo generavimo laiką.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6722">This event captures file render time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6723">Šis įvykis padeda išlaikyti failo generavimo veikimo patikrą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6723">This event helps us keep file render performance in check.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6724">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6724">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6725">**Data\_AvgTime: integer** – Vidutinis laikas, per kurį seanse buvo generuotas „Visio“ piešimo vaizdas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6725">**Data\_AvgTime: integer** - Average time it took to render Visio drawing in a session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6726">**Data\_CompositeSurfEnabled: bool** – „ True“, jei įgalintas sudėtinis vaizdo generavimo režimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6726">**Data\_CompositeSurfEnabled: bool** - true is composite rendering mode is enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6727">**Data\_Count: integer** – Laikas, kada „Visio“ generuoja piešimo seanso vaizdą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6727">**Data\_Count: integer** - Number of time Visio renders the drawing in a session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6728">**Data\_FirstRenderTime: long** – Trukmė, skirta pirmą kartą generuoti failą, milisekundėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6728">**Data\_FirstRenderTime: long** - duration to render file on first launch in millisecond</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6729">**Data\_AvgTime: integer** – Vidutinis laikas, per kurį seanse buvo generuotas „Visio“ piešimo vaizdas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6729">**Data\_MaxTime: integer** - Max time it took to render Visio drawing in a session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6737">**Data\_DocumentId: string -** GUID failo kelias</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6737">**Data\_DocumentId: string -** GUID of file path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6738">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds: double -** Trukmė, kol atliekamas veiksmas Įrašyti kaip, milisekundėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6738">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds: double -** Duration to complete save as in millisecond</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6739">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMillisecondsSquared: double -** kvadratu pakelta reikšmė DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6739">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMillisecondsSquared: double -** squared value for DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6742">**Data\_FileIOBytesRead: int -** Perskaitytų baitų skaičius įrašant</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6742">**Data\_FileIOBytesRead: int -** total bytes read while saving</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6743">**Data\_FileIOBytesReadSquared:int -** kvadratu pakelta duomenų reikšmė\_FileIOBytesRead</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6743">**Data\_FileIOBytesReadSquared: int -** squared value of Data\_FileIOBytesRead</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6744">**Data\_FileIOBytesWritten: int -** Bendras baitų kiekis įrašant</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6744">**Data\_FileIOBytesWritten: int -** total bytes written while saving</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6746">**Data\_FileName: binary -** Dvejetainė failo vardo maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6746">**Data\_FileName: binary -** Binary Hash of file name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6748">**Data\_FileOpenEndDurationInMs: long: -** Failo atidarymo trukmė milisekundėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6748">**Data\_FileOpenEndDurationInMs: long: -** duration to open file in millisecond</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ebe0a-6766">**Data\_WasSuccessful: bool -** „True“, jei atidaryti pavyko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ebe0a-6766">**Data\_WasSuccessful: bool -** true if open as was successful</span></span>
